    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:277
translate spanish re_d1620_fe4997d6:

    # Z "Alright then, let's wait."
    Z "Muy bien, esperemos."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:280
translate spanish re_d1620_b65496b4:

    # "A short while later, the guard returns..."
    "Poco después, la guardia regresa..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:283
translate spanish re_d1620_2c68d4e7:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i} You really don't like me, do you? If stares could kill..."
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Realmente no te gusto, ¿verdad? Si las miradas pudieran matar..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:284
translate spanish re_d1620_200939a8:

    # Z "Go on, lead me to the throne room."
    Z "Vamos, llévame a la sala del trono."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:290
translate spanish d16a52_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:291
translate spanish d16a52_8358c55d:

    # Z "Something caught your eye?"
    Z "¿Algo te llamó la atención?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:294
translate spanish d16a52_0e6bb06f:

    # Li "...?!"
    Li "¡¿...?!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:298
translate spanish d16a52_4ff4220a:

    # Li "Y-yes. Don't expect me to accept what you're doing. It's wrong."
    Li "S-sí. No esperes que acepte lo que estás haciendo. Está mal."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:300
translate spanish d16a52_e7cfdd15:

    # Li "Y-yes. What you are doing to her is wrong..."
    Li "S-sí. Lo que le estás haciendo está mal..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:304
translate spanish d16a52_d006e5b2:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i} Are we still not over that?"
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i} ¿Aún no hemos superado eso?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:306
translate spanish d16a52_efa2fecb:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:309
translate spanish d16a52_4692adf2:

    # Z "Just take me to the Queen, okay? Lead the way."
    Z "Sólo llévame con la Reina, ¿vale? Tú primero."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:310
translate spanish d16a52_032c3dba_1:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:319
translate spanish d16a57_40b0aed4:

    # "Minutes later..."
    "Minutos más tarde..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:323
translate spanish d16a57_56da54cb:

    # Li "My Queen, Stalker [persistent.player_name] requests an audience."
    Li "Mi Reina, El Acechador [persistent.player_name] solicita audiencia."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:326
translate spanish d16a57_2c621811:

    # Q "Yes, yes. You can let him through."
    Q "Sí, sí. Puedes dejarlo pasar."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:327
translate spanish d16a57_9ca0061c:

    # Q "Come forth, Stalker. Let's discuss your next task."
    Q "Adelante, Acechador. Analicemos tu próxima tarea."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:330
translate spanish d16a57_390e474c:

    # Q "Oh, right... there was something you wanted to tell me, wasn't there?"
    Q "Oh, cierto... Había algo que querías decirme, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:331
translate spanish d16a57_259cff29:

    # Q "What was your name again? Laiha?"
    Q "¿Cómo era tu nombre? ¿Laiha?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:334
translate spanish d16a57_ccf32d56:

    # Li "It's L-lirah, my Queen."
    Li "Soy L-lirah, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:337
translate spanish d16a57_06315a7e:

    # Q "Good, I recognise you. Now, get on with it."
    Q "Bien, te reconozco. Ahora, sigue adelante."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:340
translate spanish d16a57_b9533e8f:

    # Q "{i}*sigh*{/i} Spit it out. What is it you want to tell me."
    Q "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Escúpelo. ¿Qué es lo que quieres decirme?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:344
translate spanish d16a57_daace42a:

    # Li "I apologize for taking your time, my Queen. But... Stalker [persistent.player_name] is inappropriate towards another guard of yours."
    Li "Pido disculpas por ocupar su tiempo, mi Reina. Pero... el Acechador [persistent.player_name] ha sido inapropiado con otra de sus guardias."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:345
translate spanish d16a57_d75be3bc:

    # Li "I believe he is abusing his standing in the palace for his advantage, my Queen."
    Li "Creo que está abusando de su posición en el palacio para su beneficio, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:348
translate spanish d16a57_0e7fbd76:

    # Q "He does... what?"
    Q "Él hace... ¿qué?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:349
translate spanish d16a57_625f3618:

    # Q "Lirah, are you talking about guard Talia?"
    Q "Lirah, ¿estás hablando de la guardia Talia?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:352
translate spanish d16a57_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:355
translate spanish d16a57_a198f24f:

    # Li "Y-yes, my Queen."
    Li "S-sí, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:358
translate spanish d16a57_19ce9f31:

    # Q "I see... {i}*sigh*{/i}"
    Q "Ya veo... {i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:359
translate spanish d16a57_9b861f4f:

    # Q "That slut..."
    Q "Esa zorra..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:360
translate spanish d16a57_dac06e2e:

    # "The male guards around you start laughing..."
    "Los guardias masculinos a tu alrededor comienzan a reírse..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:364
translate spanish d16a57_843a53d1:

    # Q "You hear that? There's not a man in this room that hasn't taken a turn with her."
    Q "¿Oyes eso? No hay un solo hombre en esta sala que no haya tenido un turno con ella."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:366
translate spanish d16a57_57354c88:

    # Q "You hear that? There is not a person in this temple who takes her actions seriously."
    Q "¿Oyes eso? No hay una sola persona en este templo que se tome en serio sus acciones."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:367
translate spanish d16a57_f4150200:

    # Q "There's a reason she's posted at the entrance, girl. She's not in a position of responsibility. You of all people should know that."
    Q "Hay una razón por la que está apostada en la entrada, chica. No tiene un puesto de responsabilidad. Tú, más que nadie, deberías saberlo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:368
translate spanish d16a57_60c05339:

    # Q "No... Talia is still with the guards because her actions in the past made her dear to my predecessor. In fact, she has been in service for considerably longer than I am Queen."
    Q "No... Talia todavía está con los guardias porque sus acciones en el pasado la hicieron querida por mi predecesor. De hecho, ella ha estado en servicio por mucho más tiempo que yo como Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:369
translate spanish d16a57_4853a492:

    # Q "Her merits of the past allow her some leeway, she doesn't abuse it maliciously and I am not bothered by it enough to change it."
    Q "Sus méritos del pasado le permiten cierto margen de maniobra, no abusa de ello maliciosamente y no me molesta lo suficiente como para cambiarlo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:373
translate spanish d16a57_52759461:

    # Li "But... my Queen, I have been taught that guards are to be respected at all times, because they represent your authority."
    Li "Pero... mi Reina, me han enseñado que los guardias deben ser respetados en todo momento, porque representan tu autoridad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:374
translate spanish d16a57_d800638b:

    # Li "When I saw him the first time, he disrespected me as well, and he walked right past me as I tried to halt him."
    Li "La primera vez que lo vi, también me faltó al respeto, y pasó de largo cuando intenté detenerlo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:378
translate spanish d16a57_0b4af914:

    # Li "Even if he seems to be respectful to you, I suggest not to work with someone who does not know to respect the autority of the Palace."
    Li "Aunque parezca respetuoso contigo, te sugiero no trabajar con alguien que no sepa respetar la autoridad de Palacio."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:381
translate spanish d16a57_b0f91cb0:

    # Q "That's enough, guard. {i}*sigh*{/i}"
    Q "Ya es suficiente, guardia. {i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:382
translate spanish d16a57_ec40c7b0:

    # Q "Stalker [persistent.player_name] and I have a lot to discuss during the arena event today."
    Q "El Acechador [persistent.player_name] y yo tenemos mucho que discutir durante el evento de la Arena de hoy."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:383
translate spanish d16a57_1d7a076b:

    # Q "I will forgive your interjection, but know this: [persistent.player_name] has served the Palace consistently unlike many other stalkers."
    Q "Perdonaré tu interrupción, pero debes saber esto: [persistent.player_name] ha servido al Palacio de manera constante, a diferencia de muchos otros acechadores."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:384
translate spanish d16a57_996a59a7:

    # Q "I forgive him his temper. As a Palace guard, when not under direct orders from me, you are invited to use your judgement and discretion, not to just apply the rules blindly."
    Q "Le perdono su temperamento. Como guardia del Palacio, cuando no estás bajo órdenes directas mías, se te invita a usar tu juicio y discreción, no a aplicar las reglas ciegamente."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:387
translate spanish d16a57_a771512c:

    # Li "Yes, my Queen. I understand..."
    Li "Sí, mi Reina. Entiendo..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:390
translate spanish d16a57_8ac33f82:

    # Q "Good girl. Now, Stalker, you and I have a lot to discuss..."
    Q "Buena chica. Ahora, Acechador, tú y yo tenemos mucho que discutir..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:391
translate spanish d16a57_56bd1a16:

    # Q "Guards, form up and escort us to the Arena."
    Q "Guardias, formen y escoltenos a la Arena."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:395
translate spanish d16a57_5e49071b:

    # Li "Also, I don't think you should trust someone who in his arrogance refused to kneel in front of y-"
    Li "Además, no creo que debas confiar en alguien que en su arrogancia se negó a arrodillarse frente a ti."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:398
translate spanish d16a57_00d999d5:

    # Q "SILENCE!!!"
    Q "¡¡¡SILENCIO!!!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:400
translate spanish d16a57_8f812146:

    # "Everyone, including the previously chuckling guards fall silent in respect, holding their breath."
    "Todos, incluidos los guardias que antes se reían entre dientes, guardan silencio con respeto y contienen la respiración."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:401
translate spanish d16a57_9df1676e:

    # Q "I've had enough. For you to repeat a mere rumor like this, in front of your Queen..."
    Q "Ya he tenido suficiente. Que repitas un simple rumor como ese, delante de tu Reina..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:404
translate spanish d16a57_7d9527ca:

    # Q "Stalker [persistent.player_name] and I have a lot to discuss..."
    Q "El Acechador [persistent.player_name] y yo tenemos mucho que discutir..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:405
translate spanish d16a57_989af5c3:

    # Q "You will guide him there and protect us. After that, we will discuss your punishment for your impertinence."
    Q "Lo guiarás hasta allí y nos protegerás. Después de eso, discutiremos tu castigo por tu impertinencia."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:408
translate spanish d16a57_8d385016:

    # Q "You are dismissed."
    Q "Puedes retirarte."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:411
translate spanish d16a57_aabb34b7:

    # Li "Yes... my Queen."
    Li "Sí, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:416
translate spanish d16a57_7d84b9dd:

    # Li "But... my Queen, shouldn't the royal Palace be against corrupt relationships between its guards and citizens?"
    Li "Pero... mi Reina, ¿no debería el Palacio Real estar en contra de las relaciones corruptas entre sus guardias y ciudadanos?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:420
translate spanish d16a57_68019447:

    # Q "Let me ask you this, guard. Did he disrespect my personal authority in any way that is punishable by law?"
    Q "Déjame preguntarte esto, guardia. ¿Le faltó el respeto a mi autoridad personal de alguna manera que esté penada por la ley?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:423
translate spanish d16a57_76a84734:

    # Li "No, my Queen."
    Li "No, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:426
translate spanish d16a57_2042f277:

    # Q "Did he disrespect you?"
    Q "¿Te faltó el respeto?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:429
translate spanish d16a57_7095b941:

    # Li "No, my Queen. He did not."
    Li "No, mi Reina. No lo hizo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:434
translate spanish d16a57_2f04d181:

    # Q "Then what are we discussing? A sexual relationship between him and a guard who I knowingly tolerate?"
    Q "Entonces ¿qué estamos discutiendo? ¿Una relación sexual entre él y una guardia que tolero conscientemente?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:435
translate spanish d16a57_0093f1bd:

    # Q "Please..."
    Q "Por favor..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:438
translate spanish d16a57_1eec98de:

    # Li "I... apologize, my Queen."
    Li "Yo... le pido disculpas, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:441
translate spanish d16a57_858fec7e:

    # Q "You are young, Lija, we seem to almost be of the same age."
    Q "Eres joven, Lirah, parece que casi tenemos la misma edad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:442
translate spanish d16a57_8bcd0112:

    # Q "I accept your apology, and I applaud your courage to speak up about a potential problem."
    Q "Acepto tus disculpas y aplaudo tu valentía al hablar sobre un problema potencial."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:443
translate spanish d16a57_992f3710:

    # Q "...even if there was none."
    Q "... incluso si no hubiera ninguno."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:444
translate spanish d16a57_e672bf7c:

    # Q "Next time, it would be wise to come to me in private, instead of embarrassing yourself in front of the court and the very person you accuse."
    Q "La próxima vez, sería prudente que acudieras a mí en privado, en lugar de avergonzarte ante el tribunal y ante la misma persona a la que acusas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:447
translate spanish d16a57_bc1dd016:

    # Q "Now, Stalker [persistent.player_name], we have a lot to discuss. For now, let's adjourn the meeting to the Arena.."
    Q "Ahora, Acechador [persistent.player_name], tenemos mucho de que discutir. Por ahora, pospongamos la reunión en la Arena."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:448
translate spanish d16a57_54df5d57:

    # Q "Lirah, you are instructed to guide him there."
    Q "Lirah, tienes instrucciones de guiarlo hasta allí."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:451
translate spanish d16a57_4da8ad89:

    # Li "Yes, my Queen."
    Li "Sí, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:457
translate spanish d16a57_2416ab51:

    # Li "Especially in a case of someone who refuses to kneel in front of the Q-"
    Li "Especialmente en el caso de alguien que se niega a arrodillarse ante la Rei..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:460
translate spanish d16a57_00d999d5_1:

    # Q "SILENCE!!!"
    Q "¡¡¡SILENCIO!!!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:462
translate spanish d16a57_57a3449b:

    # "Everyone, including the previously chuckling guards fall silent in respect."
    "Todos, incluidos los guardias que antes se reían entre dientes, guardan silencio en señal de respeto."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:465
translate spanish d16a57_9efa551b:

    # Q "I strongly advise you to reconsider your words. Stalkers are not bound to the Palace unless they voluntarily serve it..."
    Q "Le recomiendo encarecidamente que reconsidere sus palabras. Los acechaodres no están atados al Palacio a menos que lo sirvan voluntariamente..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:466
translate spanish d16a57_e8b76ad8:

    # Q "...and we do not engage in spreading malicious rumours, {i}guard{/i}..."
    Q "... y no nos dedicamos a difundir rumores maliciosos, {i}guardia{/i}... ."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:469
translate spanish d16a57_032c3dba_1:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:472
translate spanish d16a57_cde38124:

    # Q "Stalker [persistent.player_name] and I have a lot to discuss at the Arena."
    Q "El Acechador [persistent.player_name] y yo tenemos mucho que discutir en la Arena."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:473
translate spanish d16a57_4c68c053:

    # Q "You will guide him there and protect us. After that, we will talk about possible consequences for your behaviour, Lija."
    Q "Lo guiarás hasta allí y nos protegerás. Después de eso, hablaremos de las posibles consecuencias de tu comportamiento, Lirah."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:476
translate spanish d16a57_b2baa3d7:

    # Q "Make up for your mistake by dealing with him as you should have in the first place. You are dismissed."
    Q "Compensa tu error tratando con él como deberías haberlo hecho en primer lugar. Puedes retirarte."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:479
translate spanish d16a57_4da8ad89_1:

    # Li "Yes, my Queen."
    Li "Sí, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:491
translate spanish d16a72_3c86f2b3:

    # "You are eventually, in silence, escorted to the arena."
    "Finalmente, en silencio, te escoltan a la Arena."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:500
translate spanish d16a72_e1bbd31d:

    # Li "My Queen, we have arrived..."
    Li "Mi Reina, ya llegamos..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:506
translate spanish d16a72_9a6482d7:

    # Li "Your Stalker is waiting outside. I will let him through."
    Li "Tu Acechador te espera fuera. Le dejaré pasar."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:511
translate spanish d16a72_d9d6d0d6:

    # "You approach the Queen..."
    "Te acercas a la Reina..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:514
translate spanish d16a72_abdc3d76:

    # Q "Hello again."
    Q "Hola de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:517
translate spanish d16a72_7d1a6098:

    # Z "I had forgotten the games were due today. So, what is it you want to discuss?"
    Z "Se me había olvidado que los juegos eran para hoy. Entonces, ¿qué es lo que quieres discutir?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:520
translate spanish d16a72_e3935b70:

    # Q "Let's... take a minute, shall we?"
    Q "Tomemos... un minuto, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:523
translate spanish d16a72_ed4c29ea:

    # Q "Guards, you are dismissed. The matters we need to discuss are not for your ears."
    Q "Guardias, podéis retiraros. Los asuntos que tenemos que discutir no son para vuestros oídos."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:524
translate spanish d16a72_9ec07aeb:

    # Q "Belay that. The young guard will stay. The rest of you go."
    Q "Anula eso. La joven guardia se queda. El resto, podéis iros."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:527
translate spanish d16a72_0b50c580:

    # G "Yes, my Queen."
    G "Sí, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:530
translate spanish d16a72_2ac5b49b:

    # Q "[persistent.player_name], my shoulders are aching. A little help?"
    Q "[persistent.player_name], me duelen los hombros. ¿Un poco de ayuda?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:533
translate spanish d16a72_eefc6e09:

    # "As you move behind her, you put your hands on her shoulders and gently massage them."
    "Mientras te mueves detrás de ella, colocas tus manos sobre sus hombros y masajeas suavemente."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:534
translate spanish d16a72_2e092ecd:

    # Z "What is on the agenda today?"
    Z "¿Qué hay en la agenda hoy?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:537
translate spanish d16a72_8304bfd0:

    # Q "Patience. The games must begin, first."
    Q "Paciencia. Los juegos deben comenzar, primero."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:540
translate spanish d16a72_e466420b:

    # Q "A rare event is about to occur today, you see?"
    Q "Hoy está a punto de ocurrir un hecho poco común, ¿lo ves?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:541
translate spanish d16a72_a90939fa:

    # Q "As you can see, even Elder Radames is coming here to hold a speech."
    Q "Como puedes ver, incluso el Elder Radamés viene aquí a pronunciar un discurso."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:544
translate spanish d16a72_88f7c329:

    # Z "The one-eyed general himself, hm. Is it important enough to interrupt him from pushing our borders ever further?"
    Z "El mismísimo general tuerto. ¿Es lo suficientemente importante como para interrumpir la expansión de nuestras fronteras?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:548
translate spanish d16a72_8bc003d0:

    # Q "Apparently so. You see..."
    Q "Aparentemente sí. Ya verás..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:549
translate spanish d16a72_fd99d373:

    # Q "Today, Elder Radames is supervising the execution of an elf."
    Q "Hoy, el Elder Radamés supervisa la ejecución de un elfo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:553
translate spanish d16a72_ba7a4151:

    # ER "CITIZENS OF OUR MAGNIFICENT STATE OF ZETA!"
    ER "¡CIUDADANOS DE NUESTRO MAGNÍFICO ESTADO DE ZETA!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:554
translate spanish d16a72_1b04bbfc:

    # ER "TODAY, WE ARE HAVING THE HONOR TO BE REMINDED OF WHAT MAKES OF US THE REALM CHOSEN BY THE GODS THEMSELVES."
    ER "HOY TENEMOS EL HONOR DE SER RECORDADOS LO QUE HACE DE NOSOTROS EL REINO ELEGIDO POR LOS MISMOS DIOSES."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:557
translate spanish d16a72_3c434fb9:

    # ER "A DEMON, A REMNANT OF THE OLD WORLD HAS BEEN FOUND."
    ER "SE HA ENCONTRADO UN DEMONIO, UN RESTO DEL VIEJO MUNDO."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:558
translate spanish d16a72_07db3af5:

    # ER "AN ARTIFACT OF THE CORRUPT PAST THAT STILL HAUNTS OUR WORLD, OVER FOUR CENTURIES AFTER THIS WORLD CRUMBLED INTO ASHES."
    ER "UN ARTEFACTO DEL PASADO CORRUPTO QUE AÚN ACECHA NUESTRO MUNDO, MÁS DE CUATRO SIGLOS DESPUÉS DE QUE ESTE MUNDO SE DESMORONARA EN CENIZAS."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:561
translate spanish d16a72_8d39b34f:

    # ER "THIS DEMON, THIS AFFRONT TO THE GODS, POLLUTES OUR EXISTENCE!"
    ER "¡ESTE DEMONIO, ESTA OFENSA A LOS DIOSES, CONTAMINA NUESTRA EXISTENCIA!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:563
translate spanish d16a72_58865149:

    # "Loud, angry booing can be heard from the crowds..."
    "Se escuchan fuertes y furiosos abucheos entre la multitud..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:566
translate spanish d16a72_3a7a9139:

    # ER "THIS... CREATURE... HAS BEEN CAUGHT SCAVENGING IN THE OUTLANDS, A STRETCH OF LAND THAT WE ARE ANNEXING TO THE STATE."
    ER "ESTA... CRIATURA... HA SIDO ATRAPADA BUSCANDO EN LAS TIERRAS EXTERIORES, UNA EXTENSIÓN DE TIERRA QUE ESTAMOS ANEXANDO AL ESTADO."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:567
translate spanish d16a72_20ba610a:

    # ER "ETERNAL LIFE! POWERS THAT WOULD MAKE THEM SEEM BETTER THAN US, SUPERIOR EVEN! THIS ABOMINATION MUST NOT STAND."
    ER "¡VIDA ETERNA! PODERES QUE LOS HARÍAN PARECER MEJORES QUE NOSOTROS, ¡INCLUSO SUPERIORES! ESTA ABOMINACIÓN NO DEBE PERMANECER."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:570
translate spanish d16a72_eddb05b5:

    # ER "NOW I ASK YOU! WHAT DO THE TEMPLE TEACHINGS TELL US SHOULD HAPPEN TO RELICS AND CREATURES FROM BEFORE THE REBIRTH OF OUR BLESSED REALM?!"
    ER "¡AHORA OS PREGUNTO! ¿QUÉ NOS ENSEÑAN LAS DOCTRINAS DEL TEMPLO SOBRE LO QUE DEBERÍA SUCEDER CON LAS RELIQUIAS Y CRIATURAS DE ANTES DEL RENACIMIENTO DE NUESTRO BENDITO REINO?!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:571
translate spanish d16a72_69882719:

    # Cr "WE - BURN - THEM!"
    Cr "¡NOSOTROS - LOS - QUEMAMOS!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:574
translate spanish d16a72_b2a50735:

    # ER "TECHNOLOGY, GENETIC ABOMINATIONS AND OTHER ANCESTRAL REMAINS HAVE PLAGUED OUR CIVILISATION SINCE ITS FOUNDING."
    ER "LA TECNOLOGÍA, ABOMINACIONES GENÉTICAS Y OTROS RESTOS ANCESTRALES HAN PLAGADO NUESTRA CIVILIZACIÓN DESDE SU FUNDACIÓN."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:575
translate spanish d16a72_bf0d55a5:

    # ER "THE CREATURES THAT ONCE INFILTRATED THIS CITY HAVE CORRUPTED ITS PEOPLE WITH COMPLACENCY AND DEVIANCY..."
    ER "LAS CRIATURAS QUE UNA VEZ SE INFILTRARON EN ESTA CIUDAD HAN CORROMPIDO A SU GENTE CON COMPLACENCIA Y DESVIACIÓN..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:578
translate spanish d16a72_ddf2d0f7:

    # ER "...AND ALMOST CAUSED ITS DEMISE."
    ER "... Y CASI PROVOCA SU DESAPARICIÓN."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:582
translate spanish d16a72_79011d7d:

    # ER "ONCE MORE, ONE OF THEM CRAWLED OUT OF THE DARKNESS."
    ER "UNA VEZ MÁS, UNO DE ELLOS SALIÓ DE LA OSCURIDAD."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:585
translate spanish d16a72_78373585:

    # ER "BE SILENT NOW, AS WE GET RID OF IT TOGETHER."
    ER "GUARDAR SILENCIO AHORA, MIENTRAS NOS DESHACEMOS DE ÉL JUNTOS."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:588
translate spanish d16a72_4c4d8dce:

    # "The crowd's fanatic chanting slowly dies down..."
    "El canto fanático de la multitud se apaga lentamente..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:593
translate spanish d16a72_a6b6038c:

    # ER "Slave, you know what must be done."
    ER "Esclava, tú sabes lo que hay que hacer."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:596
translate spanish d16a72_5bd88a00:

    # Sl "Yes, Elder Radames. On your command."
    Sl "Sí, Elder Radamés. A tus órdenes."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:598
translate spanish d16a72_6c4ec703:

    # Elf "W-wait, please don't, I BEG YOU!"
    Elf "E-espera, por favor no lo hagas, ¡TE LO RUEGO!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:601
translate spanish d16a72_a96b701d:

    # ER "It has been some time since I caught one of you..."
    ER "Hacía tiempo que no pillaba a uno de vosotros..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:602
translate spanish d16a72_d92b7cab:

    # ER "Slave... make it slow."
    ER "Esclava... hazlo lento."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:606
translate spanish d16a72_d240fc7f:

    # Elf "Please... don't. Not like this..."
    Elf "Por favor... no lo hagas. Así no..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:610
translate spanish d16a72_33e39598:

    # Elf "I don't want to die... not after all this time..."
    Elf "No quiero morir... no, después de todo este tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:614
translate spanish d16a72_2eba6ef8:

    # Elf "Ngh... please......!"
    Elf "¡Ngh... por favor... !"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:618
translate spanish d16a72_6d9f15c0:

    # Elf "Argh-"
    Elf "Argh-"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:624
translate spanish d16a72_d6f8ed55:

    # Elf "Gh-!"
    Elf "¡Gh-!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:628
translate spanish d16a72_3342ef52:

    # Elf "{i}*cough*{/i}"
    Elf "{i}*tos*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:630
translate spanish d16a72_79ff4a39:

    # ER "May you suffocate on your own blood, just as the old world suffocated under its own weight..."
    ER "Que te ahogues en tu propia sangre, igual que el viejo mundo se ahogó bajo su propio peso..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:634
translate spanish d16a72_aca3fcc9:

    # Elf "{i}*cough*{/i} Help..."
    Elf "{i}*tos*{/i} Ayuda..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:641
translate spanish d16a72_1f29ffc1:

    # Elf "Nh... {i}*sob*{/i}"
    Elf "Nh... {i}*sollozos*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:682
translate spanish d16a72_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:685
translate spanish d16a72_9234d32a:

    # Li "My Queen... May I be excused?"
    Li "Mi Reina... ¿Puedo disculparme?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:688
translate spanish d16a72_6215dc85:

    # Q "What is it now? You have seen executions before, we all have."
    Q "¿Qué pasa ahora? Ya has visto ejecuciones antes, todos las hemos visto."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:691
translate spanish d16a72_6e605a22:

    # Li "My Queen, it's... please, allow me to send in another guard for a while."
    Li "Mi Reina, es... Por favor, permítame enviar a otro guardia por un tiempo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:694
translate spanish d16a72_0f10639c:

    # Q "{i}*sigh*{/i} Fine, I will allow it this time."
    Q "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Bien, te lo permitiré esta vez."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:695
translate spanish d16a72_5344ffb6:

    # Q "You may go."
    Q "Puedes irte."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:698
translate spanish d16a72_9c31e3ac:

    # Li "Thank you, my Queen."
    Li "Gracias, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:703
translate spanish d16a72_95a8294c:

    # "She leaves, and another assumes her post..."
    "Ella se marcha y otro asume su puesto..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:706
translate spanish d16a72_555bdc6b:

    # Q "I understand that not everybody enjoys assisting an execution but it should not be so upsetting to her."
    Q "Entiendo que no a todo el mundo le gusta ayudar en una ejecución, pero a ella no debería molestarle tanto."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:707
translate spanish d16a72_81e5df67:

    # Q "This girl is roughly my age. It is time for her to grow up, if she is to stay in my service."
    Q "Esta chica tiene aproximadamente mi edad. Es hora de que crezca si quiere permanecer a mi servicio."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:712
translate spanish d16a72_84158a91:

    # Z "I agree. She seems a little too sensitive for her own good."
    Z "Estoy de acuerdo. Parece demasiado sensible para su propio bien."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:715
translate spanish d16a72_5865c203:

    # Q "If we were that sensitive, this city would eat itself."
    Q "Si fuéramos tan sensibles, esta ciudad se comería a sí misma."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:721
translate spanish d16a72_b449bbfa:

    # Z "I don't know if it was the execution itself that bothered her."
    Z "No sé si fue la ejecución en sí lo que la molestó."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:722
translate spanish d16a72_ab0e03e1:

    # Z "Maybe it was the nature of the act. The fact that this wasn't a punishment for a crime."
    Z "Quizás fue la naturaleza del acto. El hecho de que esto no era un castigo por un delito."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:725
translate spanish d16a72_dc82e289:

    # Q "That boy is everything this city condemns. His very existence was the crime. We can't make exceptions and let mutants poison our well, whether they're young, old, male or female."
    Q "Ese chico es todo lo que esta ciudad condena. Su propia existencia fue el crimen. No podemos hacer excepciones y dejar que los mutantes envenenen nuestro pozo, ya sean jóvenes, viejos, hombres o mujeres."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:728
translate spanish d16a72_3452b743:

    # Z "I grew up with the same stories. I know."
    Z "Crecí con las mismas historias. Lo sé."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:734
translate spanish d16a101x_4fdac9f3:

    # Q "Regardless, I don't want to talk politics right now."
    Q "De todos modos, no quiero hablar de política en este momento."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:735
translate spanish d16a101x_0dd45af5:

    # Q "The girl does need disciplining, especially after asking to be relieved from a simple guard duty for such a reason. I can't afford that with any guard."
    Q "La chica necesita que la disciplinen, sobre todo después de pedir que la releven de un simple deber de guardia por semejante motivo. No puedo permitírmelo con ningún guardia."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:739
translate spanish d16a101x_1ca4ebc1:

    # Q "[persistent.player_name], please go and talk some sense into her. If she's truly upset, give her the day off but tell her to use it to get her act together."
    Q "[persistent.player_name], por favor, ve y hazla entrar en razón. Si está realmente enfadada, dale el día libre, pero dile que lo aproveche para recomponerse."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:740
translate spanish d16a101x_7fb7b89e:

    # Q "Come tomorrow, if I don't see a radical adjustment in attitude, I will think of an adequate method to make her a more... dedicated guard."
    Q "Mañana, si no veo un cambio radical de actitud, pensaré en un método adecuado para convertirla en una guardia más... dedicada."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:743
translate spanish d16a101x_b429c2b1:

    # Z "You do know that she dislikes me, right? Remember what happened at the Palace?"
    Z "Sabes que no le agrado, ¿verdad? ¿Recuerdas lo que pasó en el Palacio?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:746
translate spanish d16a101x_667be335:

    # Q "I do. But I trust you will find a way, and remind her of her duties."
    Q "Sí. Pero confío en que encontrarás la manera y le recordarás sus deberes."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:749
translate spanish d16a101x_73e16acb:

    # Z "I will do as you ask."
    Z "Haré lo que me pidas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:752
translate spanish d16a101x_4ee507d0:

    # Q "Thank you."
    Q "Gracias."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:758
translate spanish d16a101x_d6b40929:

    # "You move away from the Queen's balcony..."
    "Te alejas del balcón de la Reina..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:770
translate spanish d16a102_e525d7ca:

    # Z "Hey, Lirah."
    Z "Oye, Lirah."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:773
translate spanish d16a102_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:776
translate spanish d16a102_f4164c8e:

    # Li "What do {i}you{/i} want. I don't have anything to say to you."
    Li "¿Qué {i}quieres{/i}? No tengo nada que hablar contigo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:781
translate spanish d16a102_b7fc2094:

    # Z "You complained about me just now, about the first time we met. You were right."
    Z "Te quejaste de mí hace un momento, de la primera vez que nos vimos. Tenías razón."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:782
translate spanish d16a102_573ee0e3:

    # Z "You were just doing your job, and I should have known better than to chew you out."
    Z "Tú solo estabas haciendo tu trabajo, y yo debería haber sabido que no debía reprenderte."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:783
translate spanish d16a102_04fc8050:

    # Z "I apologise."
    Z "Pido disculpas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:786
translate spanish d16a102_95925e51:

    # Li "Fine, but that doesn't change anything."
    Li "Bien, pero eso no cambia nada."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:789
translate spanish d16a102_25eed3ae:

    # Li "You're just doing what everyone else does. Abusing their power in a corrupt system."
    Li "Simplemente estás haciendo lo que hacen todos los demás. Abusar de tu poder en un sistema corrupto."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:790
translate spanish d16a102_eb1e9ccd:

    # Li "I was taught something different when I was brought here."
    Li "Me enseñaron algo diferente cuando me trajeron aquí."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:793
translate spanish d16a102_3cf11edf:

    # Z "What do you mean?"
    Z "¿Qué quieres decir?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:796
translate spanish d16a102_0d0e2d31:

    # Li "I'm not stupid! The Queen is supposed to protect the Palace, and the Guards protect her!"
    Li "¡No soy estúpida! ¡Se supone que la Reina debe proteger el Palacio y los Guardias la protegen a ella!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:797
translate spanish d16a102_ef53b4d1:

    # Li "She's not supposed to just let anyone she wants walk over us."
    Li "Se supone que no debe dejar que quien quiera nos pase por encima."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:801
translate spanish d16a102_519c0aa6:

    # Z "Tell me what's wrong."
    Z "Dime qué te pasa."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:804
translate spanish d16a102_4fcef33c:

    # Li "Why would I?"
    Li "¿Por qué iba a hacerlo?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:807
translate spanish d16a102_fb0c119e:

    # Z "Because, right now, your future depends on it, and you know it."
    Z "Porque, ahora mismo, tu futuro depende de ello, y lo sabes."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:810
translate spanish d16a102_d15ebd98:

    # Z "You're no longer a favored guard in the Queen's eyes. And yet she sent me here to reach out to you."
    Z "Ya no eres una guardia favorita a los ojos de la Reina. Y, sin embargo, ella me envió aquí para comunicarme contigo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:811
translate spanish d16a102_34b621f9:

    # Z "Give me a reason, and maybe we can prevent this going the wrong way."
    Z "Dame una razón y tal vez podamos evitar que esto vaya por el camino equivocado."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:814
translate spanish d16a102_032c3dba_1:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:815
translate spanish d16a102_98aa66fa:

    # Z "Come on! You know a guard is not supposed to act like this."
    Z "¡Vamos! Sabes que se supone que una guardia no debe actuar así."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:816
translate spanish d16a102_f9f3e109:

    # Z "The only reason the Queen didn't put you in a dungeon is because she sees something of herself in you, because of your similar age."
    Z "La única razón por la que la Reina no te metió en un calabozo es porque ve algo de sí misma en ti, debido a tu edad similar."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:819
translate spanish d16a102_41ff0a12:

    # Li "Fine! I spoke up!..."
    Li "¡Bien! ¡He hablado!..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:820
translate spanish d16a102_b9a40680:

    # Li "But how can I not?! When I was brought here, I heard all these stories about the \"only civilized city in the lands\"."
    Li "¡¿Pero cómo no hacerlo?! Cuando me trajeron aquí, escuché todas estas historias sobre la \"única ciudad civilizada del país\"."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:823
translate spanish d16a102_0d0e2d31_1:

    # Li "I'm not stupid! The Queen is supposed to protect the Palace, and the Guards protect her!"
    Li "¡No soy estúpida! ¡Se supone que la Reina debe proteger el Palacio y los Guardias la protegen a ella!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:824
translate spanish d16a102_ef53b4d1_1:

    # Li "She's not supposed to just let anyone she wants walk over us."
    Li "Se supone que no debe dejar que quien quiera nos pase por encima."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:830
translate spanish x2_de87f0d7:

    # Li "And the Elders are there to be admired and respected for their wisdom, and not to rile up the crowd in a public execution of some unfortunate mutants."
    Li "Y los Ancianos están ahí para ser admirados y respetados por su sabiduría, y no para irritar a la multitud en una ejecución pública de algunos desafortunados mutantes."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:831
translate spanish x2_064f19dd:

    # Li "That's not why I signed up for this when I joined the army. This is all wrong."
    Li "No es por eso que me inscribí en esto cuando me uní al ejército. Todo esto está mal."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:836
translate spanish x2_053959ef:

    # Z "You're right. Things are not fair, and people sometimes choose the easy routes."
    Z "Tienes razón. Las cosas no son justas y la gente a veces elige los caminos más fáciles."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:837
translate spanish x2_1949dffd:

    # Z "This boy didn't deserve his fate, probably. But trust me, out there it's much worse."
    Z "Este chico probablemente no merecía su destino. Pero créeme, ahí fuera es mucho peor."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:838
translate spanish x2_ad1d7073:

    # Z "This is the reality we live in, and my advice is to accept this. The sooner the better, if you want to keep your position."
    Z "Esta es la realidad en la que vivimos y mi consejo es aceptarla. Cuanto antes mejor, si quieres mantener tu posición."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:841
translate spanish x2_9ccb9a98:

    # Li "I'm... not sure I want to."
    Li "Estoy... no estoy segura de querer hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:844
translate spanish x2_67db8257:

    # Z "Then what are you going to do?"
    Z "Entonces, ¿qué vas a hacer?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:848
translate spanish x2_37dd54d8:

    # Z "The system has worked for over two hundred years for a reason."
    Z "El sistema ha funcionado durante más de doscientos años por una razón."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:849
translate spanish x2_b168e51a:

    # Z "Only the strongest survive, that's the rule of these lands. And this city is no exception."
    Z "Sólo los más fuertes sobreviven, esa es la regla en estas tierras. Y esta ciudad no es una excepción."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:852
translate spanish x2_c22d5d74:

    # Li "Well, then I don't want to be a part of it maybe!"
    Li "Bueno, ¡entonces tal vez no quiera ser parte de eso!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:858
translate spanish d16a106x6_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:859
translate spanish d16a106x6_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:860
translate spanish d16a106x6_a1b642a6:

    # Z "You are... thinking of quitting."
    Z "Estás... pensando en dejarlo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:863
translate spanish d16a106x6_ec536efe:

    # Li "...!"
    Li "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:866
translate spanish d16a106x6_c7da67f7:

    # Li "That's... none of your concern!"
    Li "Eso... ¡no es de tu incumbencia!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:869
translate spanish d16a106x6_99e9097b:

    # Z "You do know that the Queen won't take such an act lightly, right? Especially after today."
    Z "Sabes que la Reina no se tomará tal acto a la ligera, ¿verdad? Especialmente después de hoy."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:870
translate spanish d16a106x6_f867ea42:

    # Li "...yes."
    Li "... Sí."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:871
translate spanish d16a106x6_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:875
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_725e6e4b:

    # Z "What else do you want to do?"
    Z "¿Qué más quieres hacer?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:878
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_2975c6b1:

    # Li "I was supposed to become a scavenger, once. Before my village got assimilated into the kingdom..."
    Li "Se suponía que alguna vez me convertiría en una carroñera. Antes de que mi pueblo fuera asimilado al reino..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:879
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_ff968d06:

    # Li "I was a child."
    Li "Yo era una niña."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:880
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_4bcfc714:

    # Li "I'm thinking about going back to that path."
    Li "Estoy pensando en volver a ese camino."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:883
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_17c01257:

    # Z "A scavenger, in the wastes?"
    Z "¿Una carroñera en los páramos?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:886
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_3be7c2ea:

    # Li "I could live in the city. Go out there and scout for metal, parts, old stuff for smelting. Earn my living this way."
    Li "Podría vivir en la ciudad. Salir y buscar metal, piezas, cosas viejas para fundir. Ganarme la vida de esa manera."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:889
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_bc7dfa63:

    # Z "It's still dangerous. The closer to old Cairo you get, the more..."
    Z "Sigue siendo peligroso. Cuanto más te acerques al Viejo Cairo, más..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:892
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_cd79b118:

    # Li "So I've heard. But I am prepared. They do teach us about this in the military."
    Li "Eso he oído. Pero estoy preparada. Nos enseñan sobre esto en el ejército."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:895
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:900
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_8078a8ff:

    # Z "You don't truly know what it's like, out there."
    Z "Realmente no sabes cómo es eso ahí fuera."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:901
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_e145aaff:

    # Z "I know you're young, and you think you can do anything you set your mind to."
    Z "Sé que eres joven y crees que puedes hacer cualquier cosa que te propongas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:904
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_cf979f9a:

    # Z "And you could too, for a few years, maybe."
    Z "Y tú también podrías, durante unos años, tal vez."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:905
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_ba21a364:

    # Z "You're probably thinking I am looking down on you. After all, I have been doing a version of what you want to do...for decades."
    Z "Probablemente estés pensando que te estoy menospreciando. Después de todo, he estado haciendo una versión de lo que tú quieres hacer... durante décadas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:906
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_7cac7828:

    # Z "But think about it this way: you would be giving up one of the safest positions in the army and replace it with a life that sees most people die young."
    Z "Pero piénsalo de esta manera: estarías renunciando a una de las posiciones más seguras en el ejército y reemplazándola por una vida en la que la mayoría de la gente muere joven."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:907
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_113d2545:

    # Z "And for what?"
    Z "¿Y para qué?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:910
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:911
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_ad2cf10b:

    # Z "Adventure? Is that what you want? Then make sure to be on duty when the Queen travels, or ask to be put on patrol in the territories."
    Z "¿Aventura? ¿Eso es lo que quieres? Entonces asegúrate de estar de servicio cuando la Reina viaje, o pide que te asignen a patrullar los territorios."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:912
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_f9e6f0c1:

    # Z "You'd at least have guaranteed meals and men and women to watch your back as you advance in the unknown."
    Z "Al menos tendrías comidas garantizadas y hombres y mujeres que te cuidarían las espaldas mientras avanzas hacia lo desconocido."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:913
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_00004a1c:

    # Z "Seriously... why give this up? Are you even sure that's what you want?"
    Z "En serio... ¿por qué renunciar a eso? ¿Estás siquiera segura de que eso es lo que quieres?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:916
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_85dbe3e5:

    # Li "...I am not! I said maybe, didn't I?"
    Li "... ¡No lo estoy! Dije que tal vez, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:919
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_032c3dba_1:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:922
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_d9d9bebc:

    # Li "I-I don't like the politics, everyone is trying to step on each other. I swore an oath to the Queen, to serve her, obey her every command, but."
    Li "No... No me gusta la política, todos intentan pisotearse unos a otros. Le hice un juramento a la Reina, servirla, obedecer todas sus órdenes, pero..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:925
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_89bc1f9f:

    # Z "You thought that standing guard, training with weapons and holding a blade put these concerns out of your mind."
    Z "Pensabas que montar guardia, entrenar con armas y empuñar una espada te quitaba estas preocupaciones de la cabeza."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:926
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_e4e48011:

    # Z "That the entanglements of the Palace wouldn't be an issue you had to confront."
    Z "Que los enredos del Palacio no fueran un problema al que tuvieras que enfrentarte."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:927
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_032c3dba_2:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:931
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_071e8274:

    # Z "You know what? Do whatever you want. You're on your own."
    Z "¿Sabes que? Haz lo que quieras. Estás sóla en esto."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:934
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_c20d9ccd:

    # Li "I always am."
    Li "Yo siempre lo estoy."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:937
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_2e583d73:

    # Z "I will let the Queen know you're considering quitting. By way of apology towards you, I will try to make her not punish you."
    Z "Le haré saber a la Reina que estás considerando renunciar. A modo de disculpa hacia ti, intentaré que ella no te castigue."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:938
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_c538a47a:

    # Z "You {i}are{/i} violating your oath towards her."
    Z "Tú {i}estás{/i} violando tu juramento hacia ella."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:941
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_032c3dba_3:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:944
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_382b1a3b:

    # Li "Thank you."
    Li "Gracias."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:949
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_799ebef0:

    # Z "Farewell, Lirah. Wherever your path may lead you, good luck. You're going to need it."
    Z "Adiós, Lirah. Dondequiera que te lleve tu camino, buena suerte. Lo vas a necesitar."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:953
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_b4f7a378:

    # Z "You'd be stupid to give it all up. The safety, the position, everything."
    Z "Serías estúpida si lo dejaras todo. La seguridad, la posición, todo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:956
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_d58aeb70:

    # Z "I suggest you report to the palace tomorrow."
    Z "Te sugiero que te presentes en palacio mañana."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:959
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_5ba18f62:

    # Li "You assume you know everything, don't know me at all!"
    Li "Asumes que lo sabes todo, ¡no me conoces en absoluto!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:962
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_5df745b8:

    # Li "We're done here. No... I am done here. You won't see me again."
    Li "Hemos terminado aquí. No... Yo he terminado aquí. No volverás a verme."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:963
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_1f67f6fc:

    # Li "Goodbye."
    Li "Adiós."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:968
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_7e3a2892:

    # Z "It's your choice."
    Z "Esa es tu elección."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:973
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_efa2fecb:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:974
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_b05bb276:

    # Z "Well..."
    Z "Bueno..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:975
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_032c3dba_4:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:976
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_6eab659a:

    # Z "If you want to find your path, I can help you, even if it's somewhere else than at the Palace, or even in the Army."
    Z "Si quieres encontrar tu camino, puedo ayudarte, incluso si está en otro lugar que no sea el Palacio o incluso en el Ejército."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:979
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_e94858ad:

    # Li "...?"
    Li "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:982
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_fc4b9f16:

    # Li "Why would you do that? And anyway, I can resign by myself, if I want to."
    Li "¿Por qué harías eso? Y de todos modos, puedo dimitir yo sola, si quiero."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:985
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_700e71ce:

    # Z "But you didn't. You're sitting on the fence, because you don't know what you're doing."
    Z "Pero no lo hiciste. Estás sentada en la valla porque no sabes lo que estás haciendo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:986
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_595ff293:

    # Z "Also, knowing the Queen, she would not accept a resignation just like that. You swore an oath to her."
    Z "Además, conociendo a la Reina, ella no aceptaría una renuncia así sin más. Le hiciste un juramento."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:987
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_047486f9:

    # Z "And where would you go with only the clothes on your back? What about equipment, rations, a pack animal?"
    Z "¿Y adónde irías sólo con la ropa que llevas puesta? ¿Qué pasa con el equipo, las raciones y un animal de carga?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:988
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_e8f1559d:

    # Z "If this is really what you want, I can take care of these things."
    Z "Si eso es realmente lo que quieres, puedo encargarme de esas cosas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:991
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_fb53da6b:

    # Z "I played a small role in your fall out of favour, so I will help you, if you let me."
    Z "Yo jugué un pequeño papel en tu caída en desgracia, así que te ayudaré, si me lo permites."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:992
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_73d075c2:

    # Z "I am going to give you two days to think about it. If you want to truly abandon your post, you will have to leave the city."
    Z "Te voy a dar dos días para que te lo pienses. Si realmente quieres abandonar tu puesto, tendrás que abandonar la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:993
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_032c3dba_5:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:994
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_cef9acac:

    # Z "If that's your choice, meet me in two days before sunset, at the outer gate of the city."
    Z "Si esa es tu elección, reúnete conmigo dos días, antes del atardecer, en la puerta exterior de la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:995
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_11df44aa:

    # Z "If you change your mind before that... come to my house and let me know."
    Z "Si cambias de opinión antes de eso... ven a mi casa y dímelo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:996
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_166f85aa:

    # Z "Understood?"
    Z "¿Entendido?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1002
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_5c9ff614:

    # "She nods."
    "Ella asiente."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1008
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_787a72b3:

    # Li "I... Should I trust you?"
    Li "Yo... ¿Debería confiar en ti?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1009
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_e5a36195:

    # Li "I don't know why you out of all people would..."
    Li "No sé por qué tú, entre todas las personas..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1012
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_6e4c2459:

    # Z "Because you were wrong about me. That's why."
    Z "Porque te equivocaste conmigo. Es solo por eso."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1013
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_9499f28b:

    # Z "See you at the gate."
    Z "Nos vemos en la puerta."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1018
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_64627332:

    # Z "Then there is only one thing you need to do."
    Z "Entonces sólo hay una cosa que debes hacer."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1019
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_b602f674:

    # Z "Wake up. The city is not perfect. Many people don't find their place in it and drift off, die young or just live miserably."
    Z "Despierta. La ciudad no es perfecta. Muchas personas no encuentran su lugar en ella y se van a la deriva, mueren jóvenes o simplemente viven miserablemente."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1020
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_43cc978d:

    # Z "But you were trained to serve the Queen. There's honour and comfort in that, not just three meals a day. So do it, unconditionally."
    Z "Pero fuiste entrenada para servir a la Reina. Hay honor y consuelo en eso, no sólo tres comidas al día. Así que hazlo, incondicionalmente."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1023
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_032c3dba_6:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1024
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_8e1fd3e1:

    # Z "Are you loyal to the Queen?"
    Z "¿Eres leal a la Reina?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1027
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_4380ae56:

    # Li "I always was."
    Li "Siempre lo fui."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1030
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_fe4ec1ff:

    # Z "You probably would like to make the city a better place. That's not a wrong thing to want."
    Z "Probablemente te gustaría hacer de la ciudad un lugar mejor. No está mal querer eso."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1031
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_9ac9d85d:

    # Z "But we must know our limits... or rather, the path we're on. Changing this place is not what you're trained to do."
    Z "Pero debemos conocer nuestros límites... o mejor dicho, el camino en el que estamos. Cambiar este lugar no es para lo que estás entrenada."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1032
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_dc48999a:

    # Z "The wasteland is a cold and dangerous place. The people are rough, brutal, especially to young women like you."
    Z "El páramo es un lugar frío y peligroso. La gente es dura y brutal, especialmente con las mujeres jóvenes como tú."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1035
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_9fe97af4:

    # Z "There is none of the comfort, coin and safety to be found, especially so as a lonely scavenger who's not even in a pack."
    Z "No se puede encontrar nada de la comodidad, dinero y seguridad, especialmente como una carroñera solitaria que ni siquiera está en una manada."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1036
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_ec3fdbf1:

    # Z "Whatever nostalgia drives you to leave, think again."
    Z "Sea cual sea la nostalgia que te impulse a irte, piénsalo de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1039
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_4e3295ca:

    # Li "...I have only a few memories from back then."
    Li "... Solo tengo unos pocos recuerdos de aquel entonces."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1042
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_032c3dba_7:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1045
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_5bff2c38:

    # Li "Fine. I will not quit."
    Li "Bien. No me rendiré."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1050
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_095444d5:

    # Z "The Queen will probably want to discipline you for your words and actions today. I will try to put a good word in, so that she at least won't demote you."
    Z "La Reina probablemente querrá disciplinarte por tus palabras y acciones de hoy. Intentaré hablar bien para que al menos no te degrade."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1051
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_762acef1:

    # Z "She may doubt your commitment."
    Z "Ella puede dudar de tu compromiso."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1054
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_36d7250b:

    # Li "Then I will prove myself."
    Li "Entonces me probaré a mí misma."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1057
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_16673d74:

    # Z "She instructed me to give you a day off. Collect yourself, and make your decision."
    Z "Ella me ordenó que te diera un día libre. Serenate y toma tu decisión."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1058
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_82e1fa5e:

    # Z "You need to be ready to accept any discipline that might come. If you're not prepared for that, now is your chance to quit."
    Z "Debes estar preparada para aceptar cualquier disciplina que pueda surgir.  Si no estás preparada para ello, ahora es tu oportunidad de dejarlo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1061
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_5162972b:

    # Z "As dangerous as that may be, both in the short or long run."
    Z "Por muy peligroso que esto pueda ser, tanto a corto como a largo plazo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1062
translate spanish d16a_lirah_discussion_ab56c28e:

    # Z "I will be seeing you, Lirah"
    Z "Hasta la vista, Lirah."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1069
translate spanish d16a82x_0348d89d:

    # "You leave her and rejoin the Queen..."
    "La dejas y te reúnes con la Reina..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1075
translate spanish d16a82x_fb4825ed:

    # Q "Were you successful?"
    Q "¿Tuviste éxito?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1079
translate spanish d16a82x_a215d1fd:

    # Z "The guard Lirah... she might resign."
    Z "La guardia Lirah... puede que dimita."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1082
translate spanish d16a82x_12cdb8c8:

    # Q "Excuse me?"
    Q "¿Perdón?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1085
translate spanish d16a82x_1072fe30:

    # Z "I suggest you let it slide. She wasn't happy with her life, and is looking for a different path."
    Z "Te sugiero que lo dejes pasar. No estaba contenta con su vida y está buscando un camino diferente."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1088
translate spanish d16a82x_0992e6c5:

    # Q "The fuck I will!"
    Q "¡Y una mierda que lo haré!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1089
translate spanish d16a82x_5516e900:

    # Q "[persistent.player_name], what would the Palace think of me if I let this act of disloyalty happen without reaction?"
    Q "[persistent.player_name], ¿qué pensaría el Palacio de mí si permitiera que este acto de deslealtad se produjera sin reaccionar?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1092
translate spanish d16a82x_4826f690:

    # Z "That she's quitting is known only by you and me. Agree with her on something inconsequential. Let it be known she's sick, or on leave."
    Z "Sólo tú y yo sabemos que ella está renunciando. Coincide con ella en algo intrascendente. Que se sepa que está enferma o de permiso."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1093
translate spanish d16a82x_ac132135:

    # Z "She'll just disappear during the leave."
    Z "Ella simplemente desaparecerá durante el permiso."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1096
translate spanish d16a82x_bdc61a01:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1099
translate spanish d16a82x_fd0754b7:

    # Q "Fine, I couldn't care less about that guard but if it becomes an issue, I will have her killed."
    Q "Bien, esa guardia no podría importarme menos, pero si se convierte en un problema, haré que la maten."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1100
translate spanish d16a82x_dea0b175:

    # Q "I will have {i}you{/i} kill her!"
    Q "¡Haré que {i}tú{/i} la mates!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1101
translate spanish d16a82x_427ddb3f:

    # Q "I will kill her myself..."
    Q "La mataré yo misma..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1104
translate spanish d16a82x_95a936dd:

    # "The Queen's angry menaces turn into a low grumbling and muttering, gradually soothed by your expert massage."
    "Las airadas amenazas de la Reina se convierten en un bajo refunfuñar y murmurar, calmado gradualmente por tu experto masaje."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1105
translate spanish d16a82x_9096d784:

    # "Finally she relents, moving on from the issue."
    "Finalmente ella cede y deja atrás el tema."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1107
translate spanish d16a82x_7036ca48:

    # Z "You will have her back next morning. I set her straight."
    Z "La tendrás de vuelta a la mañana siguiente. La he corregido."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1108
translate spanish d16a82x_869eaa95:

    # Z "She was displeased by your favoritism towards me, and how things work in this city in general."
    Z "A ella le disgustó tu favoritismo hacia mí y cómo funcionan las cosas en esta ciudad en general."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1111
translate spanish d16a82x_01a8f695:

    # Q "Like I should care about the opinion of a random guard."
    Q "Como si me importara la opinión de una guardia al azar."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1114
translate spanish d16a82x_580ed46f:

    # Q "I will think of some suitable punishment for her presumption."
    Q "Pensaré en algún castigo adecuado para su presunción."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1115
translate spanish d16a82x_3b29b0de:

    # Q "A test of her commitment."
    Q "Una prueba de su compromiso."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1116
translate spanish d16a82x_00e3fcd1:

    # Q "I am sceptical she will take it well though, but if she acts up again, we will know how to deal with her."
    Q "Aunque dudo que se lo tome bien, pero si vuelve a portarse mal, sabremos cómo tratar con ella."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1119
translate spanish d16a82x_cc68a34d:

    # Z "I reminded her that the duty of a guard is to serve her Queen unconditionally."
    Z "La recordé que el deber de una guardia es servir incondicionalmente a su Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1120
translate spanish d16a82x_df65affd:

    # Z "She is loyal to you, and always was. Those were her words, and I think she stands by them."
    Z "Ella te es leal y siempre lo fue. Esas fueron sus palabras y creo que las mantiene."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1123
translate spanish d16a82x_e7156d58:

    # Q "Alright then. I will keep this in mind."
    Q "De acuerdo. Lo tendré en cuenta."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1127
translate spanish d16a82x_8352d6bc:

    # Z "I couldn't get through to her, she's a stubborn girl."
    Z "No pude comunicarme con ella, es una chica testaruda."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1128
translate spanish d16a82x_b6c9117f:

    # Z "There is no telling what she will do."
    Z "No se puede saber lo que hará."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1131
translate spanish d16a82x_1a279660:

    # Q "{i}*sigh*{/i} I will have people find her."
    Q "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Haré que alguien la encuentre."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1134
translate spanish d16a82x_0001448f:

    # Q "Needless to say, she will be disciplined for... whatever that just was."
    Q "No hace falta decir que será disciplinada por... lo que sea que haya sido."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1135
translate spanish d16a82x_39928a07:

    # Q "After that, we shall see. But it's obvious she has no place as my guard anymore."
    Q "Después de eso, ya veremos. Pero es obvio que ya no tiene lugar como mi guardia."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1136
translate spanish d16a82x_f3674859:

    # Q "I will not be concerning myself with her for long, and neither should you."
    Q "No me ocuparé de ella por mucho tiempo, y tú tampoco deberías hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1139
translate spanish d16a82x_948d7cf5:

    # "The brutal games continue on the sands of the Arena, and you watch them together for a bit..."
    "Los brutales juegos continúan en las arenas de la Arena, y podéis verlos juntos un rato..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1143
translate spanish d16a82x_afd021ed:

    # Q "I have a question..."
    Q "Tengo una pregunta..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1144
translate spanish d16a82x_1f8471ab:

    # Q "When do you know to be more forgiving... and when to be more strict?"
    Q "¿Cuándo sabes que debes ser más indulgente... y cuándo ser más estricto?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1146
translate spanish d16a82x_79dc08e6:

    # Q "I assume Lirah is as stubborn as I was when you first knelt before me. And yet, you never lost your patience."
    Q "Supongo que Lirah es tan terca como yo cuando te arrodillaste ante mí por primera vez. Y, sin embargo, nunca perdiste la paciencia."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1148
translate spanish d16a82x_f993eef4:

    # Q "You didn't put up with my attitude from the beginning. I assume you didn't put up with Lirah's either?"
    Q "No toleraste mi actitud desde el principio. ¿Supongo que tampoco aguantaste el de Lirah?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1150
translate spanish d16a82x_b52752a1:

    # Q "I didn't think you could be this forgiving, [persistent.player_name]?"
    Q "¿No pensé que pudieras ser tan indulgente, [persistent.player_name]?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1151
translate spanish d16a82x_ccf2de89:

    # Q "I mostly ever saw your strict side..."
    Q "Casi siempre vi tu lado estricto..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1153
translate spanish d16a82x_5650f4a6:

    # Q "That's a different side I haven't seen of you... Being considerate and kind."
    Q "Ése es un lado diferente que no he visto de ti... Ser considerado y amable."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1154
translate spanish d16a82x_52c0e1af:

    # Q "Why is that?"
    Q "¿Por qué?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1156
translate spanish d16a82x_afd021ed_1:

    # Q "I have a question..."
    Q "Tengo una pregunta..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1158
translate spanish d16a82x_3b3b5a36:

    # Q "Are you always this forgiving?"
    Q "¿Siempre eres así de indulgente?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1159
translate spanish d16a82x_6a9f4858:

    # Q "I didn't treat you very well at first, and yet you were always respectful."
    Q "Al principio no te traté muy bien y, sin embargo, tú siempre fuiste respetuoso."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1160
translate spanish d16a82x_a16fc37d:

    # Q "That guard doesn't like you one bit, and yet you're standing up for her."
    Q "No le agradas ni un poco a esa guardia y aun así la estás defendiendo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1162
translate spanish d16a82x_6954a490:

    # Q "Are you always this strict?"
    Q "¿Siempre eres así de estricto?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1163
translate spanish d16a82x_d1415b09:

    # Q "You didn't put up with my attitude from the beginning. And you set that girl straight as well."
    Q "No soportaste mi actitud desde el principio. Y también le pusiste las cosas claras a esa chica."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1166
translate spanish d16a82x_900f0148:

    # Z "Hm..."
    Z "Hm..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1167
translate spanish d16a82x_d6264017:

    # "You take your time to respond..."
    "Te tomas tu tiempo para responder..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1179
translate spanish d16a82x_7bda4f21:

    # Z "I may answer this question another time. For now, I will go home, if there is nothing else for me to do."
    Z "Puede que responda esta pregunta en otro momento. Por ahora, me iré a casa, si no hay nada más que hacer."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1182
translate spanish d16a82x_11e4fe48:

    # Q "Alright... hm..."
    Q "Vale... hm..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1183
translate spanish d16a82x_d9cb8ac9:

    # Q "Well. there are a few things, but this whole affair has spoiled my mood. I say we adjourn to your next visit. Remind me to speak to you about my... former advisor Sharifa again."
    Q "Bueno, hay algunas cosas, pero todo este asunto me ha estropeado el humor. Yo digo que aplacemos la sesión hasta tu próxima visita. Recuérdame que vuelva a hablarte de mi... antigua consejera Sharifa."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1184
translate spanish d16a82x_8d04229f:

    # Q "So yes, you can go home."
    Q "Así que sí, puedes irte a casa."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1185
translate spanish d16a82x_56f38f51:

    # Q "Enjoy your afternoon, [persistent.player_name]."
    Q "Disfruta de tu tarde, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1191
translate spanish d16a82x_f34b9ade:

    # "You turn around and walk away from the arena, leaving the Queen's question unanswered."
    "Te das la vuelta y te alejas de la arena, dejando la pregunta de la Reina sin respuesta."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1199
translate spanish d16a114x3_85d5740c:

    # Z "Tell your guards to leave us alone."
    Z "Dile a tus guardias que nos dejen solos."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1200
translate spanish d16a114x3_bdc61a01:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1203
translate spanish d16a114x3_8e99628c:

    # Q "Guards? Leave us for a minute."
    Q "¿Guardias? Dejadnos un momento."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1206
translate spanish d16a114x3_0b50c580:

    # G "Yes, my Queen."
    G "Sí, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1209
translate spanish d16a114x3_b69d578a:

    # "They leave..."
    "Ellos se marchan..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1212
translate spanish d16a114x3_31eaabe7:

    # Q "Alright. They are gone."
    Q "Está bien. Se han ido."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1215
translate spanish d16a114x3_4f3e7c1f:

    # Q "Why did I have t-"
    Q "¿Por qué he tenido que...?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1218
translate spanish d16a114x3_0f1944c8:

    # Q "...!"
    Q "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1221
translate spanish d16a114x3_81bc63ec:

    # Qw "[persistent.player_name]...?!"
    Qw "¡¿[persistent.player_name]...?!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1224
translate spanish d16a114x3_a7273697:

    # Z "I have raised two girls, Queen Merneith."
    Z "He criado a dos chicas, Reina Merneith."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1225
translate spanish d16a114x3_cc9bcf4d:

    # Z "Both around your age."
    Z "Ambas de tu edad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1232
translate spanish d16a_queen_caressed_010998b3:

    # Z "I'd give anything for them. I treat them well, even if they sometimes act up..."
    Z "Daría cualquier cosa por ellas. Las trato bien, aunque a veces se porten mal..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1235
translate spanish d16a_queen_caressed_8a5d7b0b:

    # Q "[persistent.player_name]..."
    Q "[persistent.player_name]..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1236
translate spanish d16a_queen_caressed_1d08b503:

    # Z "But yes, even I have my limits. And sometimes, I do get impatient..."
    Z "Pero sí, incluso yo tengo mis límites. Y a veces me impaciento..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1239
translate spanish d16a_queen_caressed_bdc61a01:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1243
translate spanish d16a_queen_groped_0339b6b1:

    # Z "I'd give anything for them. And I will always support them."
    Z "Daría cualquier cosa por ellas. Y siempre las apoyaré."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1244
translate spanish d16a_queen_groped_bdc61a01:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1245
translate spanish d16a_queen_groped_220cd091:

    # Z "And when the girls are good, I treat them well."
    Z "Y cuando las chicas son buenas, las trato bien."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1246
translate spanish d16a_queen_groped_d082073f:

    # Z "But when they are bad, they deserve to be disciplined."
    Z "Pero cuando son malas, merecen ser disciplinadas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1249
translate spanish d16a_queen_groped_ee60f40f:

    # Q "Oh..."
    Q "Oh..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1250
translate spanish d16a_queen_groped_3e00187c:

    # "You roughly knead her tit, your hand sliding inside her dress..."
    "Amasas bruscamente su teta y deslizas tu mano dentro de su vestido..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1252
translate spanish d16a_queen_groped_51f3daf1:

    # Q "[persistent.player_name]... what... are you doing...?"
    Q "[persistent.player_name]... ¿qué... estás haciendo...?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1254
translate spanish d16a_queen_groped_b62b7b46:

    # Q "[persistent.player_name]... not here..."
    Q "[persistent.player_name]... no aquí..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1261
translate spanish d16a114x4_1010a00f:

    # Z "The fight is interesting. Hardly anyone will pay attention to you."
    Z "La pelea es interesante. Casi nadie te prestará atención."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1262
translate spanish d16a114x4_2dc930f2:

    # Z "Then again, what if one of your citizens looked really hard your way..."
    Z "Por otra parte, ¿qué pasaría si uno de tus ciudadanos mirara con atención en tu dirección..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1266
translate spanish d16a114x4_64432120:

    # Z "I wonder... how does that make you feel?"
    Z "Me pregunto... ¿Cómo te hace sentir eso?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1270
translate spanish d16a114x4_3191fa3d:

    # Z "Tell me. How does that make you feel?"
    Z "Dime. ¿Cómo te hace sentir eso?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1271
translate spanish d16a114x4_2101e06b:

    # Q "Nh..."
    Q "Nh..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1272
translate spanish d16a114x4_5a3e9ec7:

    # G "My Queen, we're coming back in as commanded."
    G "Mi Reina, volvemos a entrar como se nos ha ordenado."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1275
translate spanish d16a114x4_45e164db:

    # "The guards come inside, and you let go of her neck..."
    "Los guardias entran y tú le sueltas el cuello..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1278
translate spanish d16a114x4_bdc61a01:

    # Q "..."
    Q "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1284
translate spanish d16a114_977433dc:

    # "She is quiet, as she processes what just happened..."
    "Ella está tranquila, mientras procesa lo que acaba de pasar..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1285
translate spanish d16a114_d59b9b8b:

    # Z "Well then. I will excuse myself now and return ho-."
    Z "Bien entonces. Ahora me excusaré y volveré a ca..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1288
translate spanish d16a114_8a5d7b0b:

    # Q "[persistent.player_name]..."
    Q "[persistent.player_name]..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1291
translate spanish d16a114_577f5ecf:

    # "She takes a moment..."
    "Ella se toma un momento..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1294
translate spanish d16a114_5d1713dc:

    # Q "Ehm... the next time we meet we will talk about Sharifa... but now..."
    Q "Ehm... La próxima vez que nos veamos hablaremos de Sharifa... pero ahora..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1295
translate spanish d16a114_133fea5e:

    # Q "Please sit with me, for the rest of the match. I...."
    Q "Por favor, siéntate conmigo durante el resto del encuentro. Yo... ."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1296
translate spanish d16a114_b30b8275:

    # Q "Today, I don't want to be alone..."
    Q "Hoy no quiero estar sola..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1299
translate spanish d16a114_67762c70:

    # Z "As you wish... my Queen."
    Z "Como desees... mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1303
translate spanish d16a114_7dd809dc:

    # "You sit in silence, somewhat hidden behind her, as it would not be appropriate for her to be seen with you lounging as equals."
    "Te sientas en silencio, algo escondido detrás de ella, ya que no sería apropiado que la vieran contigo descansando como iguales."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1304
translate spanish d16a114_65ef86f1:

    # "After staying for some more time as the fights entertain the crowd, you eventually excuse yourself."
    "Después de quedarte un poco más de tiempo mientras las peleas entretienen a la multitud, finalmente te disculpas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1305
translate spanish d16a114_efe34a33:

    # "As you go, briefly, you can almost feel the gaze of the young Queen upon your back."
    "A medida que avanzas, brevemente, casi puedes sentir la mirada de la joven Reina sobre tu espalda."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1313
translate spanish d16a115_3e84e421:

    # "The sun is about to set, and you meet Lirah at the main city gate, as promised."
    "El sol está a punto de ponerse y te encuentras con Lirah en la puerta principal de la ciudad, como prometiste."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1316
translate spanish d16a115_f4528a58:

    # Li "I... guess I will spend much less time inside the city from now on."
    Li "Yo... supongo que pasaré mucho menos tiempo dentro de la ciudad a partir de ahora."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1317
translate spanish d16a115_042c3f5d:

    # Z "That is the path you have chosen."
    Z "Ese es el camino que has elegido."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1318
translate spanish d16a115_c7833439:

    # Li "I know..."
    Li "Lo sé..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1324
translate spanish d16a115_888d56b7:

    # Li "...I'm sure it will be worth it."
    Li "... Estoy segura de que valdrá la pena."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1327
translate spanish d16a115_302119a2:

    # Li "I didn't expect this, to be honest. Not from you."
    Li "No me esperaba esto, para ser honesta. No de ti."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1328
translate spanish d16a115_73b7043e:

    # Li "I barely know you, after all..."
    Li "Después de todo, apenas te conozco..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1331
translate spanish d16a115_4813f06e:

    # Z "I have raised two girls. One of them became a Stalker, like me."
    Z "He criado a dos chicas. Una de ellas se convirtió en Acechadora, como yo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1332
translate spanish d16a115_fb1b28c8:

    # Z "Some people choose the freedom of the unknown and the scorching landscape of the desert, over safety. You might just be one of them."
    Z "Algunas personas prefieren la libertad de lo desconocido y el paisaje abrasador del desierto a la seguridad. Quizás tú seas una de ellas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1333
translate spanish d16a115_82ad8396:

    # Z "Remember however, that out there, there often are no second chances, and if you mess up, you die."
    Z "Recuerda, sin embargo, que a menudo no hay segundas oportunidades y, si cometes un error, morirás."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1334
translate spanish d16a115_36c2e753:

    # Z "If it becomes overwhelming, don't go to your death just to prove how tough you are."
    Z "Si se vuelve abrumador, no vayas a la muerte sólo para demostrar lo dura que eres."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1337
translate spanish d16a115_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1338
translate spanish d16a115_26291536:

    # "She nods, a hint of a smile across her lips."
    "Ella asiente, con un atisbo de sonrisa en sus labios."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1341
translate spanish d16a115_cea1cbe7:

    # Li "I was born in the desert. I know I can do this."
    Li "Nací en el desierto. Sé que puedo hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1342
translate spanish d16a115_ad955ad3:

    # Li "You can visit me soon and see yourself! I will be near the old factories close to the Cairo outskirts."
    Li "¡Podrás visitarme pronto y comprobarlo por ti mismo! Estaré cerca de las antiguas fábricas, cerca de las afueras del Viejo Cairo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1343
translate spanish d16a115_4c022b6d:

    # Li "I was told of an oasis nearby. There should be many other scavengers like me."
    Li "Me hablaron de un oasis cercano. Debería haber muchos otros carroñeros como yo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1346
translate spanish d16a115_0424e4b4:

    # Z "I know the place. Travel safe."
    Z "Conozco el lugar. Viaja con cuidado."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1347
translate spanish d16a115_e54b8312:

    # Z "Remember that you will have to adapt your training. You're not in a platoon anymore. You're a unit of one, now. Now go find out if it's all that you want."
    Z "Recuerda que tendrás que adaptar tu entrenamiento. Ya no estás en un pelotón. Ahora eres una unidad de uno. Ahora ve y descubre si es todo lo que quieres."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1353
translate spanish d16a115_33e1a9c9:

    # Li "I may have been raised by the academy, but I was born out there."
    Li "Puede que me criaran en la academia, pero nací ahí fuera."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1354
translate spanish d16a115_5a049541:

    # Li "I can do this."
    Li "Puedo hacer esto."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1359
translate spanish d16a115_bd4337ad:

    # "She starts riding to her destination, determined and confident."
    "Ella comienza a viajar hacia su destino, decidida y segura."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1360
translate spanish d16a115_2e4c6f30:

    # "While she looks content with her choice, you can't help wondering whether you've given her a leg up or a quicker path to her demise."
    "Si bien parece contenta con su elección, no puedes evitar preguntarte si le has dado una ventaja o un camino más rápido hacia su desaparición."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1363
translate spanish d16a115_ba84744f:

    # "Whatever happens now is up to her. She decided to trade away the safety of the city walls for her dreams."
    "Lo que pase ahora depende de ella. Decidió cambiar la seguridad de las murallas de la ciudad por sus sueños."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1364
translate spanish d16a115_370d9ea8:

    # "You know that the only peace and solace to be found in the desert are those one brings with them, and you wonder if this is the last time you'll ever see her..."
    "Sabes que la única paz y consuelo que se puede encontrar en el desierto son los que uno trae consigo, y te preguntas si esta será la última vez que la verás..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1375
translate spanish d16a142_84aa894f:

    # "You travel to the familiar location. The sky is darker here, but only slightly affected by the city's red mist."
    "Viajas al lugar familiar. El cielo es más oscuro aquí, pero sólo ligeramente afectado por la niebla roja de la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1378
translate spanish d16a142_3672b086:

    # "Lirah's camel is drinking from the oasis, and the ruins of an old factory stretch towards the horizon."
    "El camello de Lirah bebe del oasis y las ruinas de una antigua fábrica se extienden hacia el horizonte."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1379
translate spanish d16a142_491e9516:

    # "Scavengers of the wasteland search these remains for anything useful or valuable. Whether it's gears, machinery, or parts."
    "Los carroñeros del páramo buscan en estos restos algo útil o valioso. Ya sean engranajes, maquinaria o piezas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1380
translate spanish d16a142_d34d7528:

    # "Those who work for the city, however, like Lirah, have in theory a simpler task."
    "Quienes trabajan para la ciudad, sin embargo, como Lirah, tienen en teoría una tarea más sencilla."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1387
translate spanish d16a142_e94858ad:

    # Li "...?"
    Li "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1390
translate spanish d16a142_67995bfb:

    # Liw "Who is...?"
    Liw "¿Quién es...?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1393
translate spanish d16a142_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1400
translate spanish d16a142_04fccbe0:

    # Z "You've done well for yourself. This is an impressive place you managed to put together!"
    Z "Lo has hecho bien. ¡Este es un lugar impresionante que lograste armar!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1403
translate spanish d16a142_4a6fdc5a:

    # Z "Hey, is everything alright?"
    Z "Oye, ¿todo está bien?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1406
translate spanish d16a142_1f44b406:

    # Li "Y-yes... I think it's just... I had a long day, you know."
    Li "S-sí... Creo que es sólo... Tuve un día largo, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1409
translate spanish d16a142_3b6d069c:

    # Z "Let's sit down."
    Z "Vamos a sentarnos."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1412
translate spanish d16a142_29464a0a:

    # "As you sit in front of the former guard, you notice her frowning face and scruffed up skin."
    "Al sentarte frente a la ex guardia, notas su rostro con el ceño fruncido y su piel desaliñada."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1413
translate spanish d16a142_62e95fa2:

    # "She must have worked hard today. In fact, every day since she took her first step on this journey."
    "Ella debe haber trabajado duro hoy. De hecho, todos los días desde que dio su primer paso en este viaje."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1416
translate spanish d16a142_c3a986cf:

    # Z "How are you faring out here? It must be rough."
    Z "¿Cómo te va por aquí? Debe ser duro."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1419
translate spanish d16a142_b88a9ba5:

    # Li "I am getting by alright. It's hard work, compared to being a guard..."
    Li "Me las estoy arreglando bien. Es un trabajo duro, comparado con ser una guardia..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1420
translate spanish d16a142_3a46b624:

    # Li "...but I am free, I guess. No one is telling me when to get to work anymore. I have to tell myself, now."
    Li "... pero soy libre, supongo. Ya nadie me dice cuándo tengo que ir a trabajar. Ahora tengo que decírmelo a mí misma."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1423
translate spanish d16a142_f09b527d:

    # Z "And how is the work? Is it what you remembered, what you imagined?"
    Z "¿Y cómo es el trabajo? ¿Es lo que recordaste, lo que imaginaste?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1426
translate spanish d16a142_032c3dba_1:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1429
translate spanish d16a142_27cf89c8:

    # Li "It's interesting, and yes, it is how I remembered it. Except it's a lot harder work, back breaking, really..."
    Li "Es interesante y sí, así es como lo recordaba. Excepto que es un trabajo mucho más duro, agotador, de verdad..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1432
translate spanish d16a142_0a74d9d5:

    # Li "Whenever I go through the ruins, I can't help but imagine how people worked back then. How different life must've been."
    Li "Cada vez que paso por las ruinas, no puedo evitar imaginar cómo trabajaba la gente en aquel entonces. Qué diferente debe haber sido la vida."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1433
translate spanish d16a142_4f49b924:

    # Li "I've been finding interesting devices, and gears! I wish I could learn to make something with them."
    Li "¡He estado encontrando dispositivos y engranajes interesantes! Ojalá pudiera aprender a hacer algo con ellos."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1434
translate spanish d16a142_51be3012:

    # Li "But... {i}*sigh*{/i} thanks to the city's policies, it's all destined to be smelted, I guess."
    Li "Pero... {i}*suspiro*{/i} gracias a las políticas de la ciudad, supongo que todo está destinado a ser fundido."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1435
translate spanish d16a142_e38b4234:

    # Li "At least I get paid."
    Li "Al menos a mí me pagan."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1436
translate spanish d16a142_3c545946:

    # "She sits in silence, contemplating and you let her process things at her own speed."
    "Ella se sienta en silencio, contempla y la dejas procesar las cosas a su propio ritmo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1437
translate spanish d16a142_7b9c37ff:

    # Li "You know, I'm really jealous of you having your own vehicle and all. I'd love to build my own."
    Li "Sabes, estoy muy celosa de que tengas tu propio vehículo y todo eso. Me encantaría construir el mío propio."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1438
translate spanish d16a142_30b3f8f5:

    # Z "{i}*chuckles*{/i} Yeah. My situation is an exception really. It's the one concession to technology that is afforded to Stalkers."
    Z "{i}*risilla*{/i} Sí. Mi situación es realmente una excepción. Es la única concesión a la tecnología que se les otorga a los Acechadores."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1439
translate spanish d16a142_6c6b8c86:

    # Z "I still wouldn't be able to reach the city with it, you know."
    Z "Todavía no podría llegar a la ciudad con él, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1440
translate spanish d16a142_b6f2d838:

    # Li "That's true..."
    Li "Eso es cierto..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1441
translate spanish d16a142_dfc9205e:

    # Z "Of course the raiders from Adira don't have that restriction, nor the settlements a bit further out."
    Z "Por supuesto, los asaltantes de Adira no tienen esa restricción, ni tampoco los asentamientos un poco más alejados."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1444
translate spanish d16a142_57cd7266:

    # Z "What about the camp? How are the other scavengers treating you?"
    Z "¿Qué pasa con el campamento? ¿Cómo te tratan los otros carroñeros?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1445
translate spanish d16a142_b7713928:

    # Z "Have you had any encounters with wastelanders?"
    Z "¿Has tenido algún encuentro con los habitantes del páramo?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1446
translate spanish d16a142_8b29d934:

    # Li "None came here from the wastes, no. At least not so far."
    Li "Ninguno vino aquí desde los páramos, no. Al menos no hasta ahora."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1447
translate spanish d16a142_bc85cd54:

    # Li "We only work inside areas controlled by the royal army. I assume ramping up the Zetan patrols has worked to some extent."
    Li "Sólo trabajamos dentro de áreas controladas por el ejército real. Supongo que aumentar las patrullas Zetan ha funcionado hasta cierto punto."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1448
translate spanish d16a142_c9bce760:

    # Li "The others around here... hm..."
    Li "Los demás por aquí... hm..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1449
translate spanish d16a142_4156096a:

    # Li "Rough, stronger guys. They laughed at me when I set up camp. Said I should go home before I got hurt."
    Li "Chicos duros y más fuertes. Se rieron de mí cuando instalé el campamento. Me dijeron que me fuera a casa antes de que me hiciera daño."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1450
translate spanish d16a142_96ea8555:

    # Li "So I prefer to work alone. I don't trust them. And the way they look at me..."
    Li "Por eso prefiero trabajar sola. No confío en ellos. Y la forma en que me miran..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1453
translate spanish d16a142_da73058e:

    # Li "I mean... even when I am smeared with dirt and oil like now, it doesn't matter, you know?"
    Li "Quiero decir... incluso cuando estoy manchada de suciedad y aceite como ahora, no importa, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1454
translate spanish d16a142_e22ed0d2:

    # Li "They still leer at me."
    Li "Todavía me miran de reojo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1459
translate spanish d16a142_6e296e68:

    # Z "Did they try to lay a hand on you?"
    Z "¿Intentaron ponerte la mano encima?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1460
translate spanish d16a142_3d41be91:

    # Li "No, because I stay away from most of them. Some of them are... less troublesome than others."
    Li "No, porque me mantengo alejada de la mayoría de ellos. Algunos de ellos son... menos problemáticos que otros."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1461
translate spanish d16a142_1c3fc12b:

    # Li "Regardless, I stayed by myself since I came here."
    Li "De todos modos, me quedé sola desde que llegué aquí."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1465
translate spanish d16a142_fe2433ee:

    # Z "You will face more such challenges, repeatedly. The wasteland is rough, and not everybody is happy to be isolated at all times."
    Z "Te enfrentarás a más desafíos de ese tipo, repetidamente. El terreno baldío es accidentado y no todo el mundo está contento de estar aislado en todo momento."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1466
translate spanish d16a142_5d43e8da:

    # Z "They're alone most of the time. And there isn't really anyone trying to stop them if they get something in their minds..."
    Z "Están solos la mayor parte del tiempo. Y realmente no hay nadie tratando de detenerlos si se les ocurre algo..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1470
translate spanish d16a142_000adae0:

    # Z "They see a young and attractive girl out here. It doesn't matter if she has dirt on her."
    Z "Ven a una chica joven y atractiva por aquí. No les importa si tiene suciedad encima."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1471
translate spanish d16a142_9e7d5d59:

    # Z "All they see is a woman. They probably haven't had a woman for years."
    Z "Todo lo que ven es una mujer. Probablemente hace años que no tienen una mujer."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1475
translate spanish d16a158_1595d413:

    # Z "So don't try to reason with them, okay? If they can't keep their hands to themselves, make them."
    Z "Así que no intentes razonar con ellos, ¿vale? Si no pueden mantener las manos quietas, oblígalos."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1476
translate spanish d16a158_068dcc07:

    # Li "Yes. I am still a trained fighter..."
    Li "Sí. Todavía soy una luchadora entrenada..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1482
translate spanish d16a158_330b0e72:

    # Li "Anyway, thank you for checking in on me."
    Li "De todos modos, gracias por venir a verme."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1483
translate spanish d16a158_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1486
translate spanish d16a158_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1487
translate spanish d16a158_c98873b2:

    # "As you look into her eyes, you see a mixture of fear, insecurity, and sadness."
    "Cuando la miras a los ojos, ves una mezcla de miedo, inseguridad y tristeza."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1488
translate spanish d16a158_53bc39d9:

    # "You suspect she might be finding her new life more of a challenge than she anticipated, leaving her wondering if she's made the right choice."
    "Sospechas que su nueva vida podría estar resultando más desafiante de lo que esperaba, lo que la hace preguntarse si ha tomado la decisión correcta."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1489
translate spanish d16a158_5b4b7b65:

    # "It brings you back to when you first started to explore around the city, on your first solo outings."
    "Te devuelve a cuando empezaste a explorar la ciudad, en tus primeras salidas en solitario."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1490
translate spanish d16a158_5b07593f:

    # Z "You can always quit, Lirah. Come with me and we can get you home."
    Z "Siempre puedes dejarlo, Lirah. Ven conmigo y podemos llevarte a casa."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1492
translate spanish d16a158_663f790c:

    # Li "I want to make this work, [persistent.player_name]. I have thought about this for years. I can do it."
    Li "Quiero que esto funcione, [persistent.player_name]. He pensado en esto durante años. Puedo hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1495
translate spanish d16a158_30401e91:

    # Z "You are strong willed, Lirah. And you want to be free, and find your own path."
    Z "Eres de carácter fuerte, Lirah. Y quieres ser libre y encontrar tu propio camino."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1496
translate spanish d16a158_b28caf11:

    # Z "My [persistent.da] is the same."
    Z "Mi [persistent.da] es igual."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1497
translate spanish d16a158_e99d6a35:

    # Z "But if you're always on edge, are you really free? Can you really enjoy your freedom?"
    Z "Pero si siempre estás al límite, ¿eres realmente libre? ¿Puedes disfrutar realmente de tu libertad?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1500
translate spanish d16a158_88945767:

    # "You take out a sword..."
    "Sacas una espada..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1503
translate spanish d16a158_dda674a1:

    # Z "This is one of her blades."
    Z "Esta es una de sus espadas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1506
translate spanish d16a158_9a3962c0:

    # Z "It's lighter than your average sword. And it is especially sharp, if you keep it clean and maintain the edge."
    Z "Es más ligera que una espada normal. Y está especialmente afilada, si la mantienes limpia y conservas el filo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1507
translate spanish d16a158_e6e327b4:

    # Z "You were a guard. But the wasteland is more ruthless than any kind of trespasser you might have to deal with in the Palace."
    Z "Eras una guardia. Pero el páramo es más despiadado que cualquier tipo de intruso con el que tengas que lidiar en el Palacio."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1508
translate spanish d16a158_32e58161:

    # Z "Don't stab. Your blade might get stuck. Slash at the legs. Most people don't protect them too well, or aim for the eyes to blind the attacker."
    Z "No apuñales. Tu hoja podría atascarse. Da un tajo en las piernas. La mayoría de la gente no las protege demasiado bien, o apunta a los ojos para cegar al atacante."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1511
translate spanish d16a158_032c3dba_1:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1514
translate spanish d16a158_836a3da4:

    # Li "I... understand, thank you. I hope I won't need it."
    Li "Yo... entiendo, gracias. Espero no necesitarla."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1520
translate spanish d16a158_245a6e8d:

    # Z "You will need it. It is only a matter of time."
    Z "Lo necesitarás. Es solo cuestión de tiempo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1521
translate spanish d16a158_a42f80cb:

    # Z "Stay vigilant of your surroundings, and let them know you're not a pushover, when you need to."
    Z "Mantente atenta a tu entorno y hazles saber que no eres fácil de convencer cuando sea necesario."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1522
translate spanish d16a158_62371a73:

    # Z "See you again, Lirah."
    Z "Nos vemos de nuevo, Lirah."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1526
translate spanish d16a158_a29b8f04:

    # "You slowly walk towards your car and return home..."
    "Caminas lentamente hacia tu coche y regresas a casa..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1537
translate spanish d16a246_4848402e:

    # Z "{i}*sigh*{/i} Let's see what today will bring."
    Z "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Veamos lo que nos depara el día de hoy."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1540
translate spanish d16a246_cfbc9a5d:

    # "You Stroll a while through the market. The sky is clear, and the market is buzzing with activity."
    "Paseas un rato por el mercado. El cielo está despejado y el mercado está lleno de actividad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1543
translate spanish d16a246_5fcbb5c7:

    # "As you walk towards the gate, you spot a girl sitting by a stall. She looks rough."
    "Mientras caminas hacia la puerta, ves a una chica sentada junto a un puesto. Tiene un aspecto tosco."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1544
translate spanish d16a246_17e627b0:

    # "It takes you a few seconds before you recognise her"
    "Tardas unos segundos en reconocerla."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1547
translate spanish d16a246_39e94fd5:

    # Z "Hey Lirah. What are you doing here?"
    Z "Oye, Lirah. ¿Qué haces por aquí?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1550
translate spanish d16a246_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1551
translate spanish d16a246_2dbd9578:

    # Z "You look badly bruised."
    Z "Pareces muy magullada."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1554
translate spanish d16a246_8e98d7c2:

    # Li "It's... not as bad as it looks."
    Li "Esto... no es tan malo como parece."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1555
translate spanish d16a246_ec01ad25:

    # Li "I just need to sit down for a bit..."
    Li "Sólo necesito sentarme un rato..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1558
translate spanish d16a246_eb59e9c5:

    # "Her eyes convey a mixture of disappointment and hurt."
    "Sus ojos transmiten una mezcla de decepción y dolor."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1561
translate spanish d16a246_b95ac35e:

    # Z "Tell me what happened."
    Z "Cuéntame qué te ha pasado."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1564
translate spanish d16a246_a77248d3:

    # Li "It was... as you said. Only a matter of time."
    Li "Fue... como dijiste. Sólo era cuestión de tiempo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1565
translate spanish d16a246_cb410e47:

    # Li "I was in the ruins, when one of the other scavengers came at me, and..."
    Li "Estaba en las ruinas, cuando uno de los otros carroñeros vino hacia mí, y..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1568
translate spanish d16a246_37a7d193:

    # Li "He's dead now. And he didn't get to do what... he wanted."
    Li "Ahora está muerto. Y no pudo hacer lo que... quería."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1569
translate spanish d16a246_9d08551d:

    # Li "It's just how things are, as you said."
    Li "Así son las cosas, como dijiste."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1572
translate spanish d16a246_032c3dba_1:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1575
translate spanish d16a246_1fb4574b:

    # Z "I'm sorry to hear this."
    Z "Siento mucho oír eso."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1576
translate spanish d16a246_9c9d88d7:

    # Z "But you went through enough, don't you think?"
    Z "Pero ya pasaste por suficiente, ¿no crees?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1579
translate spanish d16a246_027f51a0:

    # Z "I don't know what exactly happened out there, but you're in Zeta."
    Z "No sé qué pasó exactamente ahí fuera, pero estás en Zeta."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1580
translate spanish d16a246_ad0f9b40:

    # Z "You're in no condition to go out in the desert right now. So rest, recuperate before you try your luck again."
    Z "No estás en condiciones de salir al desierto ahora mismo. Así que descansa, recupérate antes de volver a probar suerte."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1583
translate spanish d16a246_8996bd36:

    # Li "But that's how I earn my living. I can't afford to just lounge about."
    Li "Pero así es como me gano la vida. No puedo darme el lujo de holgazanear."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1586
translate spanish d16a246_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1587
translate spanish d16a246_94ce4f32:

    # "You think for a second..."
    "Piensas por un segundo..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1588
translate spanish d16a246_0a805613:

    # Z "You can actually. I will tell Talia to pick you up tonight and give you a hand."
    Z "De hecho, puedes. Le diré a Talia que te recoja esta noche y te eche una mano."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1589
translate spanish d16a246_31a1d245:

    # Z "Your expenses are covered for a while. I will see to it."
    Z "Tus gastos están cubiertos por un tiempo. Yo me ocuparé de ello."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1592
translate spanish d16a246_a018cb52:

    # Li "But..."
    Li "Pero..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1595
translate spanish d16a246_fc10a060:

    # Li "You don't need to do this. We still barely know each other, and I hav-"
    Li "No es necesario que hagas esto. Todavía apenas nos conocemos y tengo..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1598
translate spanish d16a246_6e9bc422:

    # Z "You barely know anyone. You're a lone wolf, but a wounded one."
    Z "Apenas conoces a nadie. Eres una loba solitaria, pero herida."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1599
translate spanish d16a246_61ed117a:

    # Z "I let you go out there to find yourself, not to get yourself killed."
    Z "Te dejé salir para encontrarte a ti misma, no para que te mataran."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1600
translate spanish d16a246_65de1143:

    # Z "You're going with Talia. You'd know she cares for you, if you didn't keep everybody at arms length."
    Z "Ve con Talia. Sabrías que ella se preocupa por ti si no mantuvieras a todos a distancia."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1603
translate spanish d16a246_032c3dba_2:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1606
translate spanish d16a246_73f041d7:

    # Z "I suspect you haven't yet been deleted from the city registers, so your stay in the city won't be an issue."
    Z "Sospecho que aún no te han eliminado de los registros de la ciudad, por lo que tu estancia en la ciudad no será un problema."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1607
translate spanish d16a246_3fd58fbd:

    # Z "Just be around, when Talia comes looking for you at the end of her shift. It's best if you don't show yourself on Palace grounds, just in case. I'll go let her know."
    Z "Solo quédate cerca cuando Talia venga a buscarte al final de su turno. Es mejor que no te presentes en los terrenos del Palacio, por si acaso. Iré a avisarla."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1611
translate spanish d16a246_c4905b18:

    # "You walk away, to follow up on your promises. Inside the Palace, you spot Talia, and approach her."
    "Te alejas para cumplir tus promesas. Dentro del Palacio, ves a Talia y te acercas a ella."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1614
translate spanish d16a246_78ed9199:

    # Ta "Hey, handsome. What brings you here today?"
    Ta "Hola, guapo. ¿Qué te trae por aquí hoy?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1617
translate spanish d16a246_dff917e5:

    # Z "I am just passing through and need to talk to you. I have spotted her in the outside market."
    Z "Estoy de paso y necesito hablar contigo. La he visto en el mercado exterior."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1620
translate spanish d16a246_c2c5994e:

    # Ta "Lirah, hm? And how's she doing? She just upped and quit one day, without a warning."
    Ta "Lirah, ¿eh? ¿Y cómo está? Ella simplemente un día se levantó y lo dejó, sin avisar."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1621
translate spanish d16a246_c0013774:

    # Ta "But if you're here, I'm guessing something is wrong?"
    Ta "Pero si estás aquí, ¿supongo que algo anda mal?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1624
translate spanish d16a246_883ca270:

    # Z "It's a long story, and not important right now. What matters is that she's in a bad way and needs help."
    Z "Es una larga historia y no es importante en este momento. Lo que importa es que está mal y necesita ayuda."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1627
translate spanish d16a246_58a9a95d:

    # Ta "Damn! What happened?"
    Ta "¡Maldición! ¿Qué le pasó?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1630
translate spanish d16a246_73b72bce:

    # Z "She will tell you herself, if you're willing to help her. She needs a place to stay for a few days."
    Z "Ella misma te lo dirá, si estás dispuesta a ayudarla. Necesita un lugar donde quedarse por unos días."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1631
translate spanish d16a246_85662fbb:

    # Z "Get her back on her feet, show her some care."
    Z "Haz que se recupere, muéstrale algo de cariño."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1634
translate spanish d16a246_e2640f51:

    # Ta "You don't need to ask twice, [persistent.player_name]."
    Ta "No necesitas pedirlo dos veces, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1635
translate spanish d16a246_4caf49ae:

    # Ta "Aunt Talia is going to fix her up in no time. Where can I find her?"
    Ta "La tía Talia lo arreglará en poco tiempo. ¿Dónde puedo encontrarla?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1638
translate spanish d16a246_0f857c14:

    # Z "I told her to wait for you at the stalls near the entrance."
    Z "Le dije que te esperara en los puestos cerca de la entrada."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1641
translate spanish d16a246_0d41fa7e:

    # Ta "Perfect. I will enjoy reconnecting with her."
    Ta "Perfecto. Disfrutaré reencontrándome con ella."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1642
translate spanish d16a246_f481a9bd:

    # Ta "Is there anything else you need?"
    Ta "¿Hay algo más que necesites?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1645
translate spanish d16a246_f1214443:

    # Z "Not now. I actually have places to be."
    Z "Ahora no. De hecho, tengo lugares donde estar."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1646
translate spanish d16a246_2e19a962:

    # Z "If there are expenses, let me know. I will spot her for the time she needs. Have to go now. See you around."
    Z "Si hay gastos, házmelo saber. La cubriré el tiempo que necesite. Tengo que irme por ahora. Nos vemos."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1649
translate spanish d16a246_155371f5:

    # Ta "Alright then. I'll find her when I'm done here."
    Ta "Bien entonces. La encontraré cuando termine aquí."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1650
translate spanish d16a246_0e156eb6:

    # Ta "Oh... and since you're being so generous..."
    Ta "Ah... y ya que estás siendo tan generoso..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1651
translate spanish d16a246_45153370:

    # Ta "Why don't you come to the inner market in two days. We will be around."
    Ta "¿Por qué no vienes al mercado interior en dos días? Estaremos por allí."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1652
translate spanish d16a246_65d72fbe:

    # Ta "You know, to see how she's doing."
    Ta "Ya sabes, para ver cómo le va."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1656
translate spanish d16a246_f105b62e:

    # Ta "I'll see you then, handsome."
    Ta "Te veré entonces, guapo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1660
translate spanish d16a246_91d86faa:

    # "Once you have taken care of this issue, you go about your day and visit the people and merchants you were there to see in the first place, then, finally, you head home."
    "Una vez que te has ocupado de este asunto, sigues con tu día y visitas a las personas y a los comerciantes que fuiste a ver en primer lugar, y luego, finalmente, te diriges a casa."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1668
translate spanish d16a261_d107860e:

    # "As suggested by Talia, you head to the market, wondering how Lirah is doing by now."
    "Como te sugirió Talia, te diriges al mercado, preguntándote cómo estará Lirah a estas alturas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1671
translate spanish d16a261_b7c9e107:

    # Li "And you are really sure I... don't look ridiculous...?"
    Li "¿Y estás realmente segura de que... no luzco ridícula...?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1674
translate spanish d16a261_dd08c399:

    # Ta "Trust me girl. I know a thing or two about this."
    Ta "Confía en mí muchacha. Sé un par de cosas sobre esto."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1675
translate spanish d16a261_fcedd753:

    # Ta "When was the last time you wore a dress that wasn't dress uniform, hm?"
    Ta "¿Cuándo fue la última vez que usaste un vestido que no era uniforme de gala, hm?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1678
translate spanish d16a261_13bf6276:

    # Li "I... don't know..."
    Li "Yo... no lo sé..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1684
translate spanish d16a261_d6669107:

    # Li "Anyways... thank.. ehm... you for helping me out."
    Li "De todos modos... gracias... ehm... por ayudarme."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1685
translate spanish d16a261_eed67411:

    # Li "I feel a bit dizzy. I'm surprised you... are not?"
    Li "Me siento un poco mareada. Me sorprende que tú... ¿no lo estés?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1688
translate spanish d16a261_7d6e679a:

    # Ta "I'm just great at not showing it, Lirah."
    Ta "Es que se me da muy bien no demostrarlo, Lirah."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1693
translate spanish d16a261_c91a7c77:

    # "You approach the women, and Talia looks over to you..."
    "Te acercas a las mujeres y Talia te mira..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1694
translate spanish d16a261_6ed48636:

    # Zt "Now that's a sight I didn't expect."
    Zt "Esa es una vista que no me esperaba."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1697
translate spanish d16a261_1b9c1860:

    # Ta "Hello, Stalker. Fancy meeting you here..."
    Ta "Hola Acechador. Qué alegría encontrarte aquí..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1700
translate spanish d16a261_4446cdb9:

    # Li "Hello, Stalker [persistent.player_name]."
    Li "Hola, Acechador [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1703
translate spanish d16a261_b2551a9a:

    # Z "Well, ladies... you look stunning. Well met."
    Z "Bueno, señoras... estáis impresionantes. Buen encuentro."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1706
translate spanish d16a261_0acf1df9:

    # Z "I didn't think I'd ever see you dolled up like this, Lirah. You look gorgeous."
    Z "No pensé que alguna vez te vería tan arreglada, Lirah. Estás impresionante."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1707
translate spanish d16a261_5a644cb3:

    # Z "The make-up suits you well."
    Z "El maquillaje te sienta bien."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1710
translate spanish d16a261_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1711
translate spanish d16a261_5f780a2f:

    # "She sways her head, averting her eyes, timidly."
    "Ella mueve la cabeza, desviando la mirada, tímidamente."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1715
translate spanish d16a261_dc7f9d7f:

    # Z "I've never seen that side of you, Lirah."
    Z "Nunca he visto ese lado tuyo, Lirah."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1718
translate spanish d16a261_600886c0:

    # Li "This was... honestly not my idea, sir."
    Li "Esto... sinceramente no fue idea mía, señor."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1721
translate spanish d16a261_fce49b23:

    # "She looks away timidly..."
    "Ella aparta la mirada tímidamente..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1727
translate spanish d16a274_b3c8e03f:

    # Ta "We've had a great night, you see. There are a few very good drinking holes, around here."
    Ta "Hemos pasado una gran noche, ya ves. Hay algunos lugares para beber muy buenos por aquí."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1730
translate spanish d16a274_11635d67:

    # Ta "...but I'd rather not want my sweet girl to go home alone."
    Ta "... pero prefiero que mi dulce niña no vuelva sola a casa."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1731
translate spanish d16a274_9fd0131f:

    # Ta "Do you mind lending her an arm to steady herself on?"
    Ta "¿Te importaría prestarle un brazo para que se mantenga firme?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1734
translate spanish d16a274_1fae868f:

    # Ta "You know how these guys will look when they see a petite cutie like her leave the city gates..."
    Ta "Ya sabes cómo se quedarán esos tipos cuando vean a una preciosidad como ella salir por las puertas de la ciudad..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1737
translate spanish d16a274_48c2f822:

    # Ta "What do you think? I'm sure she'd ask you herself, if she wasn't so shy."
    Ta "¿Qué opinas? Estoy segura de que ella misma te lo pediría, si no fuera tan tímida."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1740
translate spanish d16a274_98e9bfd7:

    # Z "If that's the case, I guess I should help."
    Z "Si ese es el caso, supongo que debería ayudar."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1743
translate spanish d16a274_a57fe0b5:

    # Z "Want to come? It's getting colder by the minute."
    Z "¿Quieres venir? Cada vez hace más frío."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1746
translate spanish d16a274_f3bf69d9:

    # Ta "He's right, you know. I do live here. You still have a little further to go..."
    Ta "El está en lo cierto, sabes. Yo vivo aquí. Aún te queda un poco más por recorrer..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1749
translate spanish d16a274_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1750
translate spanish d16a274_3e9655e7:

    # "She smiles."
    "Ella sonríe."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1753
translate spanish d16a274_32c7e6c5:

    # Z "You're stumbling a bit. Just lean on me, will you?"
    Z "Estás tambaleándote un poco. Sólo apóyate en mí, ¿quieres?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1754
translate spanish d16a274_fd6bf24c:

    # Li "Okay."
    Li "De acuerdo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1757
translate spanish d16a274_6b9b1a81:

    # Z "I'm glad that cut didn't leave a scar."
    Z "Me alegro que ese corte no haya dejado cicatriz."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1760
translate spanish d16a274_d2e180f9:

    # Li "It might have, if it wasn't for you two..."
    Li "Podría haberlo hecho, si no fuera por vosotros dos..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1763
translate spanish d16a274_2a712de9:

    # Zt "She looks much more relaxed. What a nice sight."
    Zt "Ella parece mucho más relajada. Qué bonita vista."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1766
translate spanish d16a274_ee718354:

    # Ta "Get home and sleep it off. I'll come by again tomorrow."
    Ta "Vete a casa y duerme la mona. Mañana vendré otra vez."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1769
translate spanish d16a274_59e8097b:

    # Li "Goodnight, Talia."
    Li "Buenas noches, Talia."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1772
translate spanish d16a274_f0e98e7c:

    # Ta "And you..."
    Ta "Y tú..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1775
translate spanish d16a274_5062ff6c:

    # Ta "...owe me one. If you know what I mean."
    Ta "... me debes una. Si sabes a lo que me refiero."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1778
translate spanish d16a274_01ffd315:

    # Z "I'll make sure to throughly thank you next time I see you."
    Z "Me aseguraré de agradecértelo de todo corazón la próxima vez que te vea."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1779
translate spanish d16a274_93ce3df4:

    # "You wink at her..."
    "La guiñas un ojo..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1782
translate spanish d16a274_d6025bf8:

    # Z "We're here? This is the place Talia found for you?"
    Z "¿Ya estamos aquí? ¿Éste es el lugar que Talia encontró para ti?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1783
translate spanish d16a274_b7996e1d:

    # Li "Yes... um..."
    Li "Sí... um..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1784
translate spanish d16a274_3d106255:

    # Li "Can you..."
    Li "¿Puedes..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1785
translate spanish d16a274_16fa607a:

    # Li "Just come inside, just to talk?"
    Li "... venir dentro, sólo para hablar?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1786
translate spanish d16a274_549bcda8:

    # Z "After you."
    Z "Después de ti."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1790
translate spanish d16a274_08806040:

    # Z "That's... impressive."
    Z "Eso es impresionante."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1793
translate spanish d16a274_d74eab23:

    # Z "You do know what will happen if the guards see this stuff, right?"
    Z "Sabes lo que pasará si los guardias ven esto, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1794
translate spanish d16a274_dc1be214:

    # Li "Yes..."
    Li "Sí..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1797
translate spanish d16a274_df3fcb0e:

    # Li "But what's the point of scavenging if you get rid of the interesting parts?"
    Li "Pero, ¿de qué sirve hurgar en la basura si te deshaces de las partes interesantes?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1800
translate spanish d16a274_4786d718:

    # Z "You don't need to tell me. I do this for a living."
    Z "No es necesario que me lo digas. Hago esto para ganarme la vida."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1803
translate spanish d16a274_f51f6ae1:

    # Z "I see why it's hard for you to quit. Ever thought of becoming a Stalker yourself?"
    Z "Ya veo por qué te cuesta dejarlo. ¿Alguna vez pensaste en convertirte en una Acechadora?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1806
translate spanish d16a274_bad88df0:

    # Li "I... think I'd rather avoid the Zones. Exploring those is what's required, isn't it?"
    Li "Yo... creo que prefiero evitar las Zonas. Explorarlas es lo que hace falta, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1807
translate spanish d16a274_51d0401d:

    # Z "Mummies, Raiders and Zones, yes... that's an unavoidable part of it, for most of us. They don't like it when you step on their turf."
    Z "Momias, Asaltantes y Zonas, sí... esa es una parte inevitable, para la mayoría de nosotros. No les gusta que pises su territorio."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1810
translate spanish d16a274_6d9c4ec6:

    # Li "I see... I think I'd rather not, then."
    Li "Ya veo... entonces creo que preferiría no hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1813
translate spanish d16a274_8a4ccb76:

    # Z "So scavenging it is, then? Even after what happened back there?"
    Z "Entonces, ¿hay que rebuscar? ¿Incluso después de lo que pasó allí?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1816
translate spanish d16a274_20227f61:

    # Li "To be honest... I don't know anymore."
    Li "Para ser honesta... ya no lo sé."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1817
translate spanish d16a274_3813f6df:

    # Li "I guess I just wanted to do something that had some purpose, where I didn't feel like part of a clockwork, where I did my own thing."
    Li "Supongo que sólo quería hacer algo que tuviera algún propósito, donde no me sintiera parte de un reloj, donde hiciera lo mío."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1820
translate spanish d16a274_bbb36aeb:

    # Li "But in the end, I kept working for the city, only collecting what they wanted me to collect. A glorified errand girl."
    Li "Pero al final seguí trabajando para la ciudad, recolectando solo lo que ellos querían que recolectara. Una chica de los recados glorificada."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1823
translate spanish d16a274_769a3790:

    # Z "I should tell you about the time I ended up fighting through a bunch of Raiders because the Queen had her eyes set on a statue of a cat."
    Z "Debería contarte la vez que acabé luchando contra un montón de Asaltantes porque la Reina tenía los ojos puestos en la estatua de un gato."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1826
translate spanish d16a274_43797408:

    # Li "{i}*giggles*{/i}"
    Li "{i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1827
translate spanish d16a274_36a1fbe3:

    # Z "Same difference, really."
    Z "La misma diferencia, en realidad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1830
translate spanish d16a274_1ac1d44d:

    # Li "Anyways... as I said, I don't know what I will be doing, really."
    Li "De todos modos... como te dije, no sé qué haré, de verdad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1831
translate spanish d16a274_5838015c:

    # Li "I will continue earning my living with it, for now. But I will be more careful, and stick to the safer regions."
    Li "Seguiré ganándome la vida con ello, por ahora. Pero seré más cuidadosa y me limitaré a las regiones más seguras."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1834
translate spanish d16a274_96c4161c:

    # Z "That's good to hear."
    Z "Me alegro de oírlo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1837
translate spanish d16a274_8d991f49:

    # Li "If you want, you can sleep in this room? It's my spare bed, I usually sleep in the other room."
    Li "Si quieres, ¿puedes dormir en esta habitación? Es mi cama extra, normalmente yo duermo en la otra habitación."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1838
translate spanish d16a274_9e734f67:

    # Li "You could head out in the morning. I know you live a ways outside the city."
    Li "Podrías irte por la mañana. Sé que vives lejos de la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1839
translate spanish d16a274_102a98d3:

    # Z "I could do that."
    Z "Podría hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1842
translate spanish d16a274_6e736e6c:

    # "You reach the bed..."
    "Llegas a la cama..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1845
translate spanish d16a274_8a1afac5:

    # Z "Ah... I could use a rest."
    Z "Ah... me vendría bien un descanso."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1848
translate spanish d16a274_21bd9eb2:

    # "She takes a seat at your feet..."
    "Ella se sienta a tus pies..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1849
translate spanish d16a274_8148f198:

    # Li "Hey, uhm..."
    Li "Oye, eh..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1852
translate spanish d16a274_1f04fc9a:

    # Li "About Talia..."
    Li "Sobre Talia..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1853
translate spanish d16a274_6f7528c7:

    # Li "How did it start between you two?"
    Li "¿Cómo empezó todo entre vosotros?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1854
translate spanish d16a274_5bc94973:

    # Li "You know, the way you interact with each other..."
    Li "Ya sabes, la forma en que interactuáis entre vosotros..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1858
translate spanish d16a274_37a65ee0:

    # Z "We understand each other, and she knows how I work."
    Z "Nos entendemos, y ella sabe cómo trabajo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1859
translate spanish d16a274_f695dc78:

    # Z "That said, we are old friends. Don't read too much into it."
    Z "Dicho eso, somos viejos amigos. No lo pienses demasiado."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1864
translate spanish d16a274_7354bec6:

    # Z "That was a long time ago. I remember I walked down a hallway to the Palace, and she was standing guard, not much different than today."
    Z "Eso fue hace mucho tiempo. Recuerdo que caminé por un pasillo hacia el Palacio y ella estaba haciendo guardia, no muy diferente a hoy."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1865
translate spanish d16a274_d5f1b73c:

    # Z "I was really pent up for some reason I don't remember. So I made a move. She was pregnant at the time. Already showing."
    Z "Estaba muy reprimido por alguna razón que no recuerdo. Así que hice un movimiento. Ella estaba embarazada en ese momento. Ya se le notaba."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1866
translate spanish d16a274_3678af76:

    # Z "I guess I lucked out. The hormones decided for her, and she didn't care to be caught, even if she was on duty."
    Z "Supongo que tuve suerte. Las hormonas decidían por ella y no le importaba que la descubrieran, incluso si estaba de servicio."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1869
translate spanish d16a274_e0ee8515:

    # Li "I just... saw how rough you were to her. And I was wondering why that is."
    Li "Es que... vi lo brusco que fuiste con ella. Y me preguntaba por qué."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1870
translate spanish d16a274_d301405f:

    # Li "I disliked you for how you treated her. I thought you were nothing but a brute."
    Li "Me caías mal por cómo la tratabas. Pensaba que no eras más que un bruto."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1871
translate spanish d16a274_a5e0497f:

    # Li "But then, towards me, you're very caring. I didn't know you had this other side in you."
    Li "Pero claro, conmigo eres muy cariñoso. No sabía que tenías ese otro lado en ti."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1877
translate spanish d16a274_40afce04:

    # Z "It was a long time ago. I remember walking down a hallway to the Palace."
    Z "Fue hace mucho tiempo. Recuerdo caminar por un pasillo hacia el Palacio."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1878
translate spanish d16a274_8b094ccb:

    # Z "Talia was standing guard. She didn't look very threatening, especially with her belly starting to show her pregnancy."
    Z "Talia estaba haciendo guardia. No parecía muy amenazadora, especialmente cuando su barriga empezaba a mostrar su embarazo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1879
translate spanish d16a274_1465745c:

    # Z "I was pent up, and young, and careless. So I took her."
    Z "Estaba reprimido, y era joven y descuidado. Así que me la llevé."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1882
translate spanish d16a274_b6cd9514:

    # Z "I grabbed her ponytail, put her on her knees, and well... let's say she didn't really put up a fight."
    Z "Agarré su cola de caballo, la puse de rodillas y bueno... digamos que ella realmente no se resistió."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1883
translate spanish d16a274_032c3dba_1:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1890
translate spanish d16a305_70f12d3a:

    # Li "I see... it's just... you're very confident with her."
    Li "Veo... es solo que... eres muy seguro con ella."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1891
translate spanish d16a305_20bb30c9:

    # Z "She always had her eye on me. But I have a wife, waiting at home."
    Z "Siempre me tuvo en la mira. Pero tengo una esposa que me espera en casa."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1892
translate spanish d16a305_032c3dba:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1893
translate spanish d16a305_6c8edd98:

    # Z "Why do you ask?"
    Z "¿Por qué lo preguntas?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1895
translate spanish d16a305_013f92e5:

    # Li "Would you... have done the same to me, in time?"
    Li "¿Habrías... hecho lo mismo conmigo, a su debido tiempo?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1896
translate spanish d16a305_39446469:

    # Li "You said back then, that I'd end up following Talia's example."
    Li "Dijiste en aquel entonces que terminaría siguiendo el ejemplo de Talia."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1897
translate spanish d16a305_f4ec4261:

    # Z "I guess I expected you to."
    Z "Supongo que esperaba que lo hicieras."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1898
translate spanish d16a305_032c3dba_1:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1899
translate spanish d16a305_80318e94:

    # Z "But you proved to be different. And now, we are here."
    Z "Pero demostraste ser diferente. Y ahora estamos aquí."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1900
translate spanish d16a305_6c8edd98_1:

    # Z "Why do you ask?"
    Z "¿Por qué lo preguntas?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1902
translate spanish d16a305_a442c674:

    # Li "You seem to have... a lot of experience."
    Li "Parece que tienes... mucha experiencia."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1903
translate spanish d16a305_265332c6:

    # Li "Are you like this... only with her?"
    Li "¿Eres así... sólo con ella?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1906
translate spanish d16a305_85a2a87b:

    # Z "Only with those who want it, or deserve it. You'd be surprised to find out how many women are into being... rough."
    Z "Sólo con las que lo desean o lo merecen. Te sorprendería saber a cuántas mujeres les gusta ser... rudas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1907
translate spanish d16a305_6c8edd98_2:

    # Z "Why do you ask?"
    Z "¿Por qué lo preguntas?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1910
translate spanish d16a305_d0988cf4:

    # Li "I... no real reason."
    Li "Yo... no hay ninguna razón real."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1913
translate spanish d16a305_032c3dba_2:

    # Li "..."
    Li "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1916
translate spanish d16a305_34d6302b:

    # Li "I ...um, wish you a good night. I should go to sleep as well."
    Li "... um, te deseo buenas noches. Yo también debería irme a dormir."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1917
translate spanish d16a305_66de81ef:

    # Z "Alright. Have a good rest. And thank you for letting me stay over."
    Z "Está bien. Que tengas un buen descanso. Y gracias por dejarme quedarme."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1920
translate spanish d16a305_e9317e91:

    # Li "It's alright. It's... the least I can do."
    Li "Esta bien. Esto es... lo menos que puedo hacer."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1923
translate spanish d16a305_c38bd453:

    # "She leaves you alone..."
    "Ella te deja solo..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:1926
translate spanish d16a305_1bc9bfe7:

    # Zt "Okay... time for a nap. [W] must be wondering what happened."
    Zt "Vale... es hora de echarse una siesta. [W] se estará preguntando qué ha pasado."

