    # Z "It doesn't know justice or morality. And you will have to adapt to it."
    Z "No conoce la justicia ni la moralidad. Y tendrás que adaptarte a ello."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2636
translate spanish d16a438_2504c0b5:

    # Z "And should you be in need for advice, or training... or even a home to rest in..."
    Z "Y si necesita asesoramiento, formación... o incluso un hogar donde descansar..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2639
translate spanish d16a438_b51ef02d:

    # Z "...then the gate to my home is open to you."
    Z "... entonces la puerta de mi casa estará abierta para ti."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2642
translate spanish d16a438_ecaeb3a5:

    # Z "I will go now. I will see you around, Lirah."
    Z "Ahora me voy. Nos vemos por ahí, Lirah."

