    Q "Y entonces, se me ocurrió una medida disciplinaria que garantizará que se solucionen ambas inquietudes."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2711
translate spanish d16a128_a9194f2c:

    # Q "You are a young woman, Lirah... And you have many, many years of servitude ahead under my rule..."
    Q "Eres una mujer joven, Lirah... Y tienes muchos, muchos años de servidumbre por delante bajo mi gobierno..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2714
translate spanish d16a128_0218a710:

    # Q "I am told that you are rather inexperienced in more ways than one..."
    Q "Me han dicho que eres bastante inexperta en más de un sentido..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2715
translate spanish d16a128_e4aa27dc:

    # Q "We're going to work on one of these ways!"
    Q "¡Vamos a trabajar en una de esas facetas!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2716
translate spanish d16a128_e08e45c7:

    # Q "You will let yourself be taken, humiliating yourself by submitting to a man of my choosing, in front of me."
    Q "Te dejarás llevar, humillándote sometiéndote a un hombre de mi elección, delante de mí."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2717
translate spanish d16a128_5206bc19:

    # Q "And if it so happens that you end up pregnant, good. Maybe motherhood will teach you something about accountability."
    Q "Y si se da la casualidad de que acabas embarazada, bien. Quizás la maternidad te enseñe algo sobre la responsabilidad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2720
