    Q "¿Crees que me ha creído, Acechador?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2768
translate spanish d16a128_1262a6d4:

    # Q "Listen, guard. Stalker [persistent.player_name] really is a valuable asset to the crown."
    Q "Escucha, guardia. El Acechador [persistent.player_name] es realmente un activo valioso para la corona."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2769
translate spanish d16a128_03baacd4:

    # Q "He has spoken up for you, asking leniency on your behalf. You will from now on be on your best behaviour around him. Understood?"
    Q "Ha hablado por ti, pidiendo clemencia en tu nombre. A partir de ahora te portarás lo mejor posible con él. ¿Entendido?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2770
translate spanish d16a128_21299150:

    # Q "Causing insult or showing disrespect or disapproval will reflect badly directly on myself and the consequences..."
    Q "Causar insultos o mostrar falta de respeto o desaprobación se reflejará mal directamente en mí y las consecuencias..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2773
translate spanish d16a128_076516dc:

    # Li "I understand. My Queen."
    Li "Entiendo. Mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2776
translate spanish d16a128_8b6b8ccd:

    # Q "Perfect! Let's make sure you don't cross me ever again, ok?"
    Q "¡Perfecto! Asegurémonos de que no vuelves a cruzarte conmigo, ¿vale?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2779
translate spanish d16a128_a153927e:

    # Q "Well then. I declare this business concluded. Now go away. I have things to do."
    Q "Pues bien. Declaro concluido este asunto. Ahora vete. Tengo cosas que hacer."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2780
translate spanish d16a128_135f0735:

    # Q "I will speak to you another time, Stalker [persistent.player_name]."
    Q "Hablaré contigo en otro momento, Acechador [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2785
translate spanish d16a128_5e30b84d:

    # Z "Soon, my Queen."
    Z "Pronto, mi Reina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2789
translate spanish d16a128_c45dd108:

    # "You return home."
    "Vuelves a casa."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2801
translate spanish re_d16a162_7bc371e6:

    # Sl "..."
    Sl "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2802
translate spanish re_d16a162_e7cd2841:

    # Q "Mh... You look exquisite. My slaves prepared you well."
    Q "Mh... Te ves exquisita. Mis esclavas te prepararon bien."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2805
translate spanish re_d16a162_240cf9f7:

    # Q "You need to know that I appreciate your commitment, Lirah."
    Q "Necesitas saber que aprecio tu compromiso, Lirah."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2806
translate spanish re_d16a162_ead309b6:

    # Q "The fact that you have accepted my decision so quickly..."
    Q "El hecho de que hayas aceptado mi decisión tan rápido..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2807
translate spanish re_d16a162_f00ccc1b:

    # Q "...this is promising."
    Q "... esto es prometedor."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2812
translate spanish re_d16a162_7b7e0917:

    # Q "Who knows, maybe you will be my greatest guard one day. Pregnant or not, as may be."
    Q "Quién sabe, tal vez algún día seas mi mejor guardia. Embarazada o no, según sea el caso."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2822
translate spanish re_d16a162_eeeafa28:

    # Sl "My Queen, the Stalker is here."
    Sl "Mi Reina, el Acechador está aquí."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2825
translate spanish re_d16a162_7f2f1bd4:

    # Q "Very well."
    Q "Muy bien."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2828
translate spanish re_d16a162_2f6d6ca4:

    # "You enter the chamber..."
    "Entras en la cámara..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2829
translate spanish re_d16a162_bcb85aed:

    # Q "Join us, [persistent.player_name]."
    Q "Únete a nosotras, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2832
translate spanish re_d16a162_e76ca9d3:

    # Q "Welcome, [persistent.player_name]. I usually use these chambers to commit a slave to such a task."
    Q "Bienvenido, [persistent.player_name]. Normalmente uso estas cámaras para encomendar a un esclavo esa tarea."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2835
translate spanish re_d16a162_48623d05:

    # Q "This time, however, is different."
    Q "Esta vez, sin embargo, es diferente."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2840
translate spanish re_d16a162_185bb3c7:

    # Li "Really him, my Queen?"
    Li "¿De verdad él, mi Reina?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:2845
translate spanish re_d16a162_770a686e:

    # Q "Really, Lirah. This is a punishment, not just a test."
