    Z "Buenas noches. No esperaba volver a verte. ¿Qué te trae por esta ciudad?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5272
translate spanish d16c17_bde62c0e:

    # Jaz "Oh, I am just helping out a friend tonight. Nothing much."
    Jaz "Oh, sólo estoy ayudando a un amigo esta noche. No es gran cosa."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5275
translate spanish d16c17_ab204b7b:

    # Jaz "Say, how did your [persistent.da] fare out there? She was heading to one of the Zones, right?"
    Jaz "Dime, ¿cómo le fue a tu [persistent.da]? Ella se dirigía a una de las Zonas, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5278
translate spanish d16c17_d9706a7b:

    # Jaz "Oh... I can see your wife smiling. I guess that's good news?"
    Jaz "Oh... puedo ver a tu mujer sonriendo. ¿Supongo que son buenas noticias?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5281
translate spanish d16c17_c6d7105c:

    # Z "That's correct. Nice of you to remember. And yes, she completed her task."
    Z "Eso es cierto. Muy amable por recordarlo. Y sí, completó su tarea."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5282
translate spanish d16c17_138159a7:

    # W "She returned to us healthy and safe, which is the most important thing."
    W "Ella regresó sana y salva, que es lo más importante."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5283
translate spanish d16c17_615798a2:

    # W "She had us scared for a while, but all went well."
    W "Nos tuvo asustados un rato, pero todo salió bien."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5286
translate spanish d16c17_88a1dde5:

    # Jaz "That is good to hear. Life is precious and the Zones.. well..."
    Jaz "Es bueno oírlo. La vida es preciosa y las Zonas... bueno..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5287
translate spanish d16c17_fa1d6a56:

    # Jaz "That said.. if you don't mind, I am closing soon, so I have to wrap things up."
    Jaz "Dicho esto... si no os importa, voy a cerrar pronto, así que tengo que terminar."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5288
translate spanish d16c17_873bfed8:

    # Jaz "Good fortune be with you, until we meet again!"
    Jaz "¡Que la suerte te acompañe, hasta que nos volvamos a encontrar!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5291
translate spanish d16c17_9058f96b:

    # Z "And with you. Thank you [Jaz]."
    Z "Y contigo. Gracias [Jaz]."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5294
translate spanish d16c17_29a2de66:

    # "She leaves..."
    "Ella se va..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5297
translate spanish d16c17_46066801:

    # W "She seemed kind. Where did you know her from? I really like her."
    W "Parecía amable. ¿De dónde la conoces? Ella me gusta mucho."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5300
translate spanish d16c17_6f0da210:

    # Z "She really is kind. [S] and I met her at the oasis, the night before she entered the zone."
    Z "Ella realmente es amable. [S] y yo la conocimos en el oasis, la noche antes de que ella ingresara a la zona."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5303
translate spanish d16c17_89d449e2:

    # Z "She has good memory. We only talked for a short time, and yet she remembers me."
    Z "Tiene buena memoria. Hablamos poco tiempo y aún así ella se acuerda de mí."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5306
translate spanish d16c17_d3bec7f9:

    # W "Yeah..."
    W "Sí..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5307
translate spanish d16c17_de12e2f1:

    # Ww "By the way, I think I've caught the attention of a guard..."
    Ww "Por cierto, creo que he llamado la atención de un guardia..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5310
translate spanish d16c17_97cbe4d2:

    # Z "You always catch people's attention, that's nothing new."
    Z "Siempre llamas la atención de la gente, eso no es nada nuevo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5313
translate spanish d16c17_a18e9a8c:

    # "You keep walking through the market. It's getting dark, and what nightlife there is in Zeta is starting to show..."
    "Sigues caminando por el mercado. Está oscureciendo y la vida nocturna que hay en Zeta empieza a mostrarse..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5314
translate spanish d16c17_578c58cf:

    # W "Oh look, that is Mandisa! Let's go greet her."
    W "¡Oh mira, esa es Mandisa! Vamos a saludarla."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5317
translate spanish d16c17_6c8cc175:

    # W "Good evening, Mandisa. How have you been?"
    W "Buenas noches, Mandisa. ¿Qué tal te ha ido?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5320
translate spanish d16c17_8e29cd15:

    # Ma "Hello [W], things are going well, thank you; and I hear that congratulations are in order?"
    Ma "Hola [W], todo va bien, gracias; y ¿he oído que hay que darte la enhorabuena?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5323
translate spanish d16c17_59b9bed2:

    # Z "You have heard, I assume?"
    Z "Supongo que te habrás enterado."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5326
translate spanish d16c17_47d7f09a:

    # Ma "I still have many friends at the Palace, and I am told that young [S] has been seen there."
    Ma "Todavía tengo muchos amigos en el Palacio, y me han dicho que han visto allí a la joven [S]."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5329
translate spanish d16c17_cdfeb3c2:

    # Z "I guess word gets around. But yes, she did well."
    Z "Supongo que se corre la voz. Pero sí, ella lo hizo bien."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5330
translate spanish d16c17_8bbc386f:

    # Z "I figure she will want to tell you all about it herself, next time you see her."
    Z "Me imagino que ella misma querrá contártelo todo la próxima vez que la veas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5333
translate spanish d16c17_058cc872:

    # Ma "I shall listen gladly. And what about you two, are you going somewhere?"
    Ma "Lo escucharé con mucho gusto. Y vosotros dos, ¿vais a alguna parte?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5336
translate spanish d16c17_2f476556:

    # W "Oh, we're having a night out. Although, I have yet to find out where my husband is taking me."
    W "Oh, estamos pasando una noche fuera. Aunque aún no sé adónde me va a llevar mi marido."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5339
translate spanish d16c17_eb7f895f:

    # Ma "Is that so? That's a coincidence. We're about to close shop and do the same thing."
    Ma "¿Realmente es así? Es una coincidencia. Nosotros estamos a punto de cerrar la tienda y hacer lo mismo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5342
translate spanish d16c17_d607b286:

    # Ma "It has been a long week. A bit of relaxation is in order."
    Ma "Ha sido una semana larga. Un poco de relajación es necesario."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5343
translate spanish d16c17_f38c0907:

    # Ma "Enjoying the services your slaves provide after work only gets you so far. Sometimes it's best to take your man and get out."
    Ma "Disfrutar de los servicios que brindan tus esclavos después del trabajo solo te lleva hasta cierto punto. A veces es mejor tomar a tu hombre y salir."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5346
translate spanish d16c17_6475599a:

    # W "Well then, maybe we will cross paths. I wish you two a pleasant evening."
    W "Pues bien, tal vez nos crucemos. Os deseo una agradable velada."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5349
translate spanish d16c17_9af73e33:

    # Ma "And the same to you. Let [S] know that I congratulate her on her achievement."
    Ma "Y lo mismo para ti. Hazle saber a [S] que la felicito por su logro."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5350
translate spanish d16c17_5e9314f4:

    # Ma "Maybe she will want to stop by some time."
    Ma "Quizá quiera pasarse por aquí alguna vez."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5357
translate spanish d16c54_fad70dcb:

    # "After a few minutes of slowly making your way through the city, you finally arrive at your destination."
    "Después de unos minutos de recorrer lentamente la ciudad, finalmente llegas a tu destino."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5361
translate spanish d16c54_ec03d089:

    # Z "Here we are..."
    Z "Aquí estamos..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5364
translate spanish d16c54_4645fe97:

    # W "Wow..."
    W "Guau..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5367
translate spanish d16c54_ec5f9aca:

    # W "We have not been here before, have we?"
    W "Aquí nunca habíamos estado, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5370
translate spanish d16c54_d0cea35c:

    # Z "The place is relatively new and I am told that it's relaxed and friendly, with great food and service."
    Z "El lugar es relativamente nuevo y me han dicho que es relajado y amigable, con excelente comida y servicio."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5371
translate spanish d16c54_938522a9:

    # W "If you look around you'll notice that the place is not for everybody's pockets."
    W "Si miras a tu alrededor, te darás cuenta de que este lugar no está al alcance de todos los bolsillos."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5372
translate spanish d16c54_20b433b0:

    # Z "I don't think so. Follow me. We have a reservation..."
    Z "No lo creo. Sígueme. Tenemos una reserva..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5375
translate spanish d16c54_8772e7a9:

    # "You sit down with your wife..."
    "Te sientas con tu mujer..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5378
translate spanish d16c54_8ff3efe4:

    # W "I like the mood in here, my love. It was a great idea."
    W "Me gusta el ambiente que hay aquí, mi amor. Ha sido una gran idea."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5381
translate spanish d16c54_2fba08ae:

    # Z "I am glad you like it."
    Z "Me alegro de que te guste."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5384
translate spanish d16c54_e5bc4fd4:

    # W "So, is this a new establishment?"
    W "Entonces, ¿se trata de un nuevo establecimiento?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5385
translate spanish d16c54_ba99af35:

    # Z "Apparently. I don't know anything else, yet."
    Z "Aparentemente. No sé nada más todavía."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5388
translate spanish d16c54_58a19c06:

    # W "Maybe we can ask one of the waitresses. I am curious about any new... fancy place in the city."
    W "Quizá podamos preguntar a una de las camareras. Tengo curiosidad por saber si hay algún sitio nuevo... elegante en la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5391
translate spanish d16c54_7a846cbb:

    # Z "Wait and see, my interrogation techniques are unmatched. Perk of the job."
    Z "Espera y verás, mis técnicas de interrogatorio son inigualables. Ventajas del trabajo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5394
translate spanish d16c54_9a7c24e8:

    # W "Ahh... I knew I didn't marry you solely for your muscles."
    W "Ahh... sabía que no me había casado contigo únicamente por tus músculos."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5395
translate spanish d16c54_7055539d:

    # W "Interrogation skills; yes, that must be the real reason."
    W "Habilidades de interrogatorio. Sí, esa debe ser la verdadera razón."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5400
translate spanish d16c54_69384cd5:

    # "Observing the other patrons of this establishment, you notice that they don't seem to exhibit the wear and tear of the common workers."
    "Observando a los demás clientes de este establecimiento, te das cuenta de que no parecen mostrar el desgaste de los trabajadores comunes."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5401
translate spanish d16c54_76039e74:

    # W "This really is an exclusive place."
    W "Este es realmente un lugar exclusivo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5404
translate spanish d16c54_1bc59ed8:

    # Z "And there comes the waitress."
    Z "Y ahí viene la camarera."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5405
translate spanish d16c54_33e96d15:

    # W "Oh my..."
    W "Oh vaya..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5408
translate spanish d16c54_2b07261e:

    # W "So... seeing all these people, nicely dressed..."
    W "Así que... ver a toda esta gente, bien vestida..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5409
translate spanish d16c54_cc3a38a8:

    # W "Do you feel a bit underdressed now?"
    W "¿No te sientes ahora un poco mal vestido?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5412
translate spanish d16c54_5c6c8d58:

    # Z "I am the dress."
    Z "Yo estoy vestido."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5413
translate spanish d16c54_89112656:

    # W "You are lucky I don't care. Can you imagine the fit my sister would have thrown?"
    W "Tienes suerte de que no me importe. ¿Te imaginas el berrinche que habría montado mi hermana?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5414
translate spanish d16c54_b29c95c2:

    # Z "One of your better qualities over her, after all."
    Z "Después de todo, una de tus mejores cualidades sobre ella."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5415
translate spanish d16c54_3b3e8e13:

    # Z "...but, maybe don't tell her that..."
    Z "... pero tal vez no le digas eso..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5416
translate spanish d16c54_413c3031:

    # W "{i}*giggles*{/i}"
    W "{i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5417
translate spanish d16c54_980975f4:

    # W "You can try and bribe me later..."
    W "Puedes intentar sobornarme más tarde..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5420
translate spanish d16c54_a28de3f3:

    # "A pregnant servant with an impressive figure approaches your table, addressing your wife."
    "Una sirvienta embarazada y de impresionante figura se acerca a tu mesa, dirigiéndose a tu mujer."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5423
translate spanish d16c54_c4446996:

    # Wa "Hello... ma'am..."
    Wa "Hola... señora..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5424
translate spanish d16c54_886f3592:

    # extend " um... "
    extend " um..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5425
translate spanish d16c54_cbf4950a:

    # extend "Welcome to our establishment."
    extend " Bienvenidos a nuestro establecimiento."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5426
translate spanish d16c54_a899f6c3:

    # Wa "Would you like something to eat?"
    Wa "¿Quieren algo de comer?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5429
translate spanish d16c54_a1133678:

    # W "Of course. So, what are the dishes we can choose from?"
    W "Por supuesto. ¿Cuáles son los platos que podemos elegir?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5430
translate spanish d16c54_5d3c0117:

    # W "It is our first time here, what would you suggest?"
    W "Es nuestra primera vez aquí, ¿qué sugerirías?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5433
translate spanish d16c54_f87019c0:

    # Wa "Oh, yes... excuse me, ma'am."
    Wa "Oh, sí... disculpe, señora."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5434
translate spanish d16c54_8f791121:

    # Wa "One of our most requested dishes is sweet potato..."
    Wa "Uno de nuestros platos más solicitados es el boniato..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5435
translate spanish d16c54_c524eb31:

    # extend " er..."
    extend " er..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5436
translate spanish d16c54_a06e95b0:

    # extend " puree with lamb with a side of spinach."
    extend " puré de cordero con una guarnición de espinacas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5437
translate spanish d16c54_a2ba5108:

    # Wa "And of course there is today's special, couscous with camel meat, roasted onions and garlic... and spices."
    Wa "Y por supuesto está el especial de hoy, cuscús con carne de camello, cebolla y ajo asados... y especias."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5438
translate spanish d16c54_4d1213a1:

    # Wa "And then of course, there is ful medames..."
    Wa "Y luego, por supuesto, están las ful medames..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5439
translate spanish d16c54_2210e378:

    # extend " uhhh... "
    extend " uhhh..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5440
translate spanish d16c54_3974200d:

    # extend " slow-cooked and seasoned fava beans, seasoned with cumin and other herbs."
    extend " habas cocidas a fuego lento y sazonadas, condimentadas con comino y otras hierbas."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5441
translate spanish d16c54_7198522e:

    # Wa "We usually recommend it more for breakfast, though..."
    Wa "Aunque normalmente lo recomendamos más para el desayuno..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5444
translate spanish d16c54_a932e947:

    # W "I will take the sweet potato puree..."
    W "Yo me quedo con el puré de boniato..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5447
translate spanish d16c54_80357188:

    # Wa "As you wish, madam."
    Wa "Como usted desee, señora."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5450
translate spanish d16c54_58e1b991:

    # Wa "Sir..."
    Wa "Señor..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5451
translate spanish d16c54_886f3592_1:

    # extend " um... "
    extend " um..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5452
translate spanish d16c54_cba9914d:

    # extend " would you like to order a dish, as well?"
    extend " ¿le gustaría pedir un plato también?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5455
translate spanish d16c54_26bfb024:

    # "You can see she's struggling, reciting her lines in a sing-songy voice..."
    "Se puede ver que está luchando, recitando sus líneas con voz cantarina..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5456
translate spanish d16c54_ec93a06c:

    # Z "They all sound delicious..."
    Z "Todos suenan deliciosos..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5457
translate spanish d16c54_18c44922:

    # Z "..I think I will have the ful medames."
    Z "... Creo que me pediré las ful medames."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5460
translate spanish d16c54_fa01b0de:

    # Wa "Excellent choice!"
    Wa "¡Excelente opción!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5465
translate spanish d16c54_09f9d21f:

    # "She walks off towards the kitchen..."
    "Ella camina hacia la cocina..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5468
translate spanish d16c54_c2c9cc07:

    # W "..."
    W "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5469
translate spanish d16c54_99980bf6:

    # Z "Hmm? What are you looking at?"
    Z "¿Mmm? ¿Qué estás mirando?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5472
translate spanish d16c54_81d40a1e:

    # Z "Oh, I see. A handsome, young waiter."
    Z "Oh, claro. Un camarero joven y guapo."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5473
translate spanish d16c54_1924d10c:

    # W "Hah... just a couple of girls that apparently are skipping straight to dessert."
    W "Ja... sólo un par de chicas que aparentemente van directo al postre."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5476
translate spanish d16c54_1be956ba:

    # Z "The place does include a few quality services."
    Z "El lugar incluye algunos servicios de calidad."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5477
translate spanish d16c54_cf236755:

    # W "Well, they do seem to cater to all tastes."
    W "Bueno, parecen satisfacer todos los gustos."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5480
translate spanish d16c54_ad37fe3f:

    # Ci "..."
    Ci "..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5481
translate spanish d16c54_cd994330:

    # Z "The brunette doesn't appear too convinced, though."
    Z "Sin embargo, la morena no parece muy convencida."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5484
translate spanish d16c54_3bfefc6a:

    # "As you discretely observe and comment on the various people sat at the tables around you, the waitress returns with your order."
    "Mientras observas y comentas discretamente a las distintas personas sentadas en las mesas de tu alrededor, la camarera vuelve con tu pedido."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5485
translate spanish d16c54_1bfecfcc:

    # Wa "Here you go."
    Wa "Aquí tienen."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5488
translate spanish d16c54_55077419:

    # Wa "We hope you will enjoy the meal."
    Wa "Esperamos que disfruten de la comida."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5491
translate spanish d16c54_a8b7c86b:

    # Wa "I am... terribly sorry, sir. But um..."
    Wa "Lo siento... muchísimo, señor. Pero em..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5492
translate spanish d16c54_cf4b4c0d:

    # Wa "I had not noticed you had empty chal..."
    Wa "No me había dado cuenta de que tenía las copas..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5493
translate spanish d16c54_723353e0:

    # extend " uh... glasses?"
    extend " eh... ¿vacías?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5496
translate spanish d16c54_917cc871:

    # W "That's... now that you mention it...?!"
    W "Eso es... ahora que lo mencionas...?!"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5497
translate spanish d16c54_c2fa747d:

    # Z "What do you recommend, then?"
    Z "¿Qué nos recomiendas entonces?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5500
translate spanish d16c54_b056441e:

    # Wa "Sir, aygar is the most requested drink. It's... usually made with yoghurt, but allow me to present a... variation."
    Wa "Señor, el aygar es la bebida más solicitada. Generalmente se hace con yogur, pero permítanme presentarles una... variación."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5503
translate spanish d16c54_c41bdb2d:

    # "[W] looks at you mischievously..."
    "[W] te mira con picardía..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5511
translate spanish re_d16c81_8b176d8b:

    # W "She does look like she could use the relief. What do you think, dear?"
    W "Parece que le vendría bien el alivio. ¿Qué opinas, querido?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5517
translate spanish re_d16c81_b7a3506f:

    # Z "Well, straight from the tap it is then."
    Z "Bueno, directamente del grifo es entonces."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5523
translate spanish re_d16c81_7083828c:

    # Z "Not today. I think we will have spiced wine instead."
    Z "Hoy no. Creo que en su lugar tomaremos vino especiado."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5526
translate spanish re_d16c81_4ee1c0ea:

    # Wa "As you wish. Allow me to get it from the kitchen, then."
    Wa "Como desee. Entonces déjame ir a buscarlo a la cocina."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5532
translate spanish d16c83_d6c03baa:

    # "She takes [W]'s chalice, and brings it up to her chest..."
    "Ella toma el cáliz de [W] y lo lleva hasta su pecho..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5535
translate spanish d16c83_230e2d16:

    # Wa "Ma'am, it will only take a second. Allow me..."
    Wa "Señora, sólo será un segundo. Permítame..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5544
translate spanish d16c83_a41f5b4c:

    # Wa "Mh..."
    Wa "Mh..."

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5545
translate spanish d16c83_8988817f:

    # Zt "...was that a moan?"
    Zt "... ¿eso ha sido un gemido?"

# game/scripts/day16.rpy:5548
translate spanish d16c83_84eee255:

